{"type":"message","id":"3b95b505","parentId":"9be76df7","timestamp":"2026-04-13T06:59:27.680Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Found the issue. The lint is failing because:\n\n1. `exam.repository.ts` has `require()` style imports (lines 35, 149) - `@typescript-eslint/no-require-imports` error\n2. `dashboard.controller.ts` has `let` instead of `const` (lines 34, 35) - `prefer-const` error\n\nThese are real lint errors that need to be fixed before the pipeline can pass.","thinkingSignature":"ebf2326c2b755e2e1d458ea9c43865b71c0f94abd1f94dd136f25f3acd21e72a"},{"type":"text","text":"**Nguyên nhân: Lint errors không pass**\n\nCI chạy `yarn lint` và thất bại với **4 lint errors**:\n\n```\nexam.repository.ts\n  35:38  error  @typescript-eslint/no-require-imports   ← require() style import\n 149:38  error  @typescript-eslint/no-require-imports   ← require() style import\n\ndashboard.controller.ts\n   34:7  error  prefer-const     ← dùng let thay vì const\n   35:7  error  prefer-const     ← dùng let thay vì const\n```\n\n**2 lỗi có thể fix tự động** bằng `yarn lint --fix`. Nhưng `require()` trong `exam.repository.ts` cần convert sang `import` thủ công.\n\n**Cách fix:**\n\n```bash\n# Auto-fix prefer-const\nyarn lint --fix\n\n# Manual fix exam.repository.ts: đổi require() → import\n```\n\nSau khi fix xong lint → push lại → pipeline chạy lại → MR mới merge được."}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":1894,"output":344,"cacheRead":49776,"cacheWrite":525,"totalTokens":52539,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776063553461,"responseId":"062bc742cbece503796f563a2c4fb419"}}
