{"type":"message","id":"eac0140d","parentId":"017b24f5","timestamp":"2026-04-13T07:01:25.640Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I have the full picture:\n\n**BE MR !9** (`fix/ci-git-pull-ff-only`): Pipeline **failed** - lint errors (exam.repository.ts + dashboard.controller.ts)\n**FE MR !12** (`fix/ci-git-pull-ff-only`): Pipeline **success** ✅\n\nSo the FE fix is ready to merge! The BE has a lint issue that needs to be fixed.\n\nThe pipeline failure on develop (2448193908) is from BEFORE MR !12 was merged. Now that MR !12's pipeline passed, the next develop pipeline should work.\n\nLet me summarize for the Lead:\n1. **FE MR !12** (`fix/ci-git-pull-ff-only`) → Pipeline ✅ **success** → ready to merge\n\n\n2. **BE MR !9** (`fix/ci-git-pull-ff-only`) → Pipeline ❌ **failed** → lint errors need fixing first\n\nThe root cause is that Orbis's direct push created a divergence in the FE's develop branch, and the git pull command in CI couldn't reconcile it without the `--ff-only` flag. Merging FE MR !12 will resolve this, but I need to address the lint errors blocking BE MR !9 first.","thinkingSignature":"c2bd9deffff6bccf3ddf1fe9b9494d423547e14a6a101ee6f327c2d58ea8f9b6"},{"type":"text","text":"**Tình hình đầy đủ:**\n\n| MR | Project | Branch | Pipeline | Vấn đề |\n|---|---|---|---|---|\n| **!12** | FE (ahv-qlhv-fe) | `fix/ci-git-pull-ff-only` | ✅ **success** | Sẵn sàng merge |\n| **!9** | BE (ahv-qlhv-be) | `fix/ci-git-pull-ff-only` | ❌ **failed** | 4 lint errors |\n\n---\n\n**Root cause:** Commit `fix/ci-git-pull-ff-only` trên cả 2 repo chưa được merge, nên CI chạy trên `develop` vẫn dùng config cũ → `git pull develop` fail vì divergent branches (do Orbis push thẳng trước đó).\n\n**FE MR !12:** Đã ✅ pass → Lead có thể merge ngay.\n\n**BE MR !9:** Đang ❌ fail lint → cần fix `exam.repository.ts` (đổi `require()` → `import`) + `dashboard.controller.ts` (`let` → `const`) trước.\n\nLead muốn Orbis fix lint trên BE branch `fix/ci-git-pull-ff-only` không?"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":292,"output":535,"cacheRead":53473,"cacheWrite":1156,"totalTokens":55456,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776063662551,"responseId":"062bc7b04910fdd87ded9f3335db5ac9"}}
