{"type":"message","id":"eef2ecf9","parentId":"4168c5ec","timestamp":"2026-04-13T07:08:17.647Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"BE MR !9 pipeline is still pending (running). FE MR !12 is success. Lead asked about the root cause - \"lỗi này do đâu\" - referring to the pipeline failure. The old pipeline failure was caused by 4 lint errors:\n1. `require()` style import in exam.repository.ts (lines 35, 149)\n2. `let` instead of `const` in dashboard.controller.ts (lines 34, 35)\n\nBut these have been fixed. The new pipeline is running. Let me confirm.","thinkingSignature":"e99a0edf19b7cbc6df46c2d9c0cc4ae621bd6401425d0ea431d9d1892854d275"},{"type":"text","text":"Pipeline cũ đã failed. Orbis đã fix rồi — commit mới đang chạy. Lead hỏi về nguyên nhân gốc của lỗi pipeline trước đó?\n\n**Root cause lỗi pipeline BE MR !9 (commit cũ `a6282e94`):**\n\n| File | Lỗi | Nguyên nhân |\n|---|---|---|\n| `exam.repository.ts:35,149` | `@typescript-eslint/no-require-imports` | Dùng `require()` bên trong method thay vì `import` ở đầu file |\n| `dashboard.controller.ts:34,35` | `prefer-const` | Khai báo biến `let` nhưng không reassign |\n\n**Đã fix** trong commit `a54a003` — đổi `require()` → `import`, `let` → `const`. Pipeline mới đang chạy.\n\n**FE MR !12:** ✅ pass, merge được ngay."}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":136,"output":352,"cacheRead":58897,"cacheWrite":2757,"totalTokens":62142,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776064087032,"responseId":"062bc95890997f33f41bf86147d2e36c"}}
