{"type":"message","id":"20e25448","parentId":"2fdf5393","timestamp":"2026-04-13T07:56:58.025Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Lead wants to set a custom git author name for the agent commits, so when code is pushed, Lead can identify which agent made the commit. I need to set git config for the workspaces where agents work.\n\nLet me set `user.name` and `user.email` for the relevant workspaces. The email could be something like `agent@openclaw.dev` with a name that identifies the agent.","thinkingSignature":"fc870f3d87dce6379bf9e39943a22fbc9f6d0c54881df56645d3f621a63f8897"},{"type":"text","text":"\n được. Orbis sẽ set git config cho workspace agents.\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_w9fql2l37hyd_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# Set git author for master-orchestrator workspace (this workspace)\ncd /root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/master-orchestrator && git config user.name \"Orbis (master-orchestrator)\" && git config user.email \"orbis@openclaw.ai\" && echo \"✅ master-orchestrator: $(git config user.name) <$(git config user.email)>\"\n\n# Also set for agent workspaces\nfor ws in senior-backend senior-frontend senior-devops senior-architect senior-qa planner; do\n  dir=\"/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/$ws\"\n  if [ -d \"$dir/.git\" ]; then\n    git -C \"$dir\" config user.name \"$ws (OpenClaw Agent)\" 2>/dev/null\n    git -C \"$dir\" config user.email \"$ws@openclaw.ai\" 2>/dev/null\n    echo \"✅ $ws: $(git -C \"$dir\" config user.name)\"\n  fi\ndone"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":232,"output":331,"cacheRead":67835,"cacheWrite":420,"totalTokens":68818,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776067005139,"responseId":"062bd4be95ee7dbf921859fceec3f9a5"}}
