{"type":"message","id":"c7144749","parentId":"e5bc5b76","timestamp":"2026-04-13T07:58:41.494Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good. Now all agent workspaces have their git identity set. When agents clone repos into their workspace and commit, they'll use their own identity.\n\nLet me summarize for the Lead.","thinkingSignature":"9939926aa3c1e4fc9446bc73a4f742fa8f8806700596e1673e2270c249700f43"},{"type":"text","text":"✅ **Đã set git author identity cho tất cả agents:**\n\n| Agent | Commit author |\n|---|---|\n| master-orchestrator | `Orbis (master-orchestrator) <orbis@openclaw.ai>` |\n| senior-backend | `senior-backend (OpenClaw Agent) <senior-backend@openclaw.ai>` |\n| senior-frontend | `senior-frontend (OpenClaw Agent) <senior-frontend@openclaw.ai>` |\n| senior-devops | `senior-devops (OpenClaw Agent) <senior-devops@openclaw.ai>` |\n| senior-architect | `senior-architect (OpenClaw Agent) <senior-architect@openclaw.ai>` |\n| senior-qa | `senior-qa (OpenClaw Agent) <senior-qa@openclaw.ai>` |\n| senior-security | `senior-security (OpenClaw Agent) <senior-security@openclaw.ai>` |\n| planner | `planner (OpenClaw Agent) <planner@openclaw.ai>` |\n\nBây giờ khi agent nào push code, commit sẽ hiển thị đúng tên agent của họ trên GitLab."}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":388,"output":301,"cacheRead":70373,"cacheWrite":747,"totalTokens":71809,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776067112167,"responseId":"062bd529bcc3e2a503dac0182f114a90"}}
