{"type":"message","id":"36abb55c","parentId":"3bc9c2f3","timestamp":"2026-04-13T07:59:11.920Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Lead wants to identify which agents are controlled by them (as opposed to maybe other users' agents). So instead of just \"senior-backend\", it should be something like \"Khuowgn-senior-backend\" or \"[Khuowgn] senior-backend\" to make it clear these are Lead's agents.","thinkingSignature":"331bd34eb4c0b159d38e781d0a9d6c67e2c999369489f6840a9c7d7d120f2180"},{"type":"text","text":"Ý tưởng hay. Orbis suggest:\n\n```\n# Format: [Owner]-[Agent] — Agent Name\n\n[Khuowgn]-senior-backend  <khuowgn.agents@ahv.dev>\n[Khuowgn]-senior-frontend <khuowgn.agents@ahv.dev>\n[Khuowgn]-planner         <khuowgn.agents@ahv.dev>\n[Khuowgn]-master-orchestrator <khuowgn.agents@ahv.dev>\n```\n\n**Ví dụ commit trên GitLab:**\n```\n[Khuowgn]-senior-backend: feat: implement auth endpoint\n[Khuowgn]-master-orchestrator: fix(git-workflow): enforce MR process\n```\n\nLead confirm format này không? Hay muốn style khác?\n\n| Option | Style |\n|--------|-------|\n| A | `[Khuowgn]-senior-backend` |\n| B | `Khuowgn.senior-backend` |\n| C | `Orbis-senior-backend` (dùng tên bot) |"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":0,"output":294,"cacheRead":70144,"cacheWrite":911,"totalTokens":71349,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776067137351,"responseId":"062bd542f937b58c9d7ca7e2bd14c6a5"}}
