{"type":"message","id":"7c6eccc5","parentId":"77ea40d5","timestamp":"2026-04-14T02:40:10.928Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good. The DTLX group session has ended. Now I understand:\n\n1. QLHV group (-5163901258) - ALREADY ENDED ✅\n2. DTLX group (-5168104492) - ALREADY ENDED ✅\n3. Cron sessions - KEEP\n4. Direct session - KEEP\n\nAll the group sessions are already ended. The Cron jobs (5p Progress, DTLX 5p, Agent Status) are system jobs and Lead probably wants to keep those running.\n\nSo the situation is:- Direct (Lead): KEEP- Cron jobs: KEEP (system health monitoring)- QLHV group: ENDED ✅- DTLX group: ENDED ✅\n\n\nI should confirm with Lead that both group sessions have already ended and the focus is on DTLX backend and frontend work, with the cron jobs running in the background to maintain ecosystem health.","thinkingSignature":"17395cb0619090db66e5532f479abebdcf077ed76ff310d01a6543746a9c55b8"},{"type":"text","text":"Rồi Lead. Tình trạng:\n\n| Session | Status |\n|---|---|\n| **QLHV group** (-5163901258) | ✅ Đã ended |\n| **DTLX group** (-5168104492) | ✅ Đã ended |\n| **Direct (Lead)** | ✅ Running |\n| **Cron jobs** | ✅ Running (health monitoring) |\n\nTất cả group sessions đã ngưng. Chỉ giữ cron health monitoring + direct Lead. Bây giờ chỉ focus vào **ahv-dtlx-backend** và **ahv-dtlx-frontend** theo yêu cầu của Lead.\n\nOrbis đang chờ Lead giao task mới."}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":981,"output":346,"cacheRead":114524,"cacheWrite":4382,"totalTokens":120233,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776134398415,"responseId":"062cdc003f26ad636fbcd46b6f54f997"}}
