{"type":"message","id":"1bf92e08","parentId":"fba9f550","timestamp":"2026-04-14T02:45:54.243Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Gateway is having issues again. Let me try spawning a fresh session instead.","thinkingSignature":"2ef9f29f085a1e6569384d6ff64bb20deaf8f82c6240a54ecc9e0c3ac2ec4594"},{"type":"text","text":"Gateway đang có vấn đề. Orbis spawn session mới thay thế:\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_lm2o7gvbzyh4_1","name":"sessions_spawn","arguments":{"task":"You are the DTLX ecosystem orchestrator (group -5168104492). Your job: test API module auth on ahv-dtlx-backend.\n\n## Project\n- **GitLab:** ahv-dtlx/ahv-dtlx-backend (77055841), ahv-dtlx/ahv-dtlx-frontend (77055851)\n- **Bot:** @thuowgn_bot in group -5168104492\n\n## Current state\n- DTLX FE: ✅ port 3000 running\n- DTLX BE: ❌ Build failed — 35+ TypeScript errors on branch feature/clean-architecture-migration\n  - Error: interface mismatch (data vs docs, limit vs itemsPerPage)\n- deploy-be subagent: timed out (SIGKILL after 451s)\n\n## Your tasks (in order)\n1. Clone/check ahv-dtlx-backend (branch feature/clean-architecture-migration or develop)\n2. Fix TypeScript compilation errors — especially interface mismatches\n3. Build successfully: yarn build\n4. Start BE server\n5. Test API module auth endpoints\n\n## Rules\n- Use AHV-Holding-DEV model (NOT TroLy — that causes 500 errors)\n- Follow Git Workflow: branch-per-task + MR for Lead review\n- Commit with [Khuowgn]-senior-backend identity\n- Log progress to memory/YYYY-MM-DD.md\n- Respond to @thuowgn_bot mentions in the group\n\n## Context\nBranch feature/clean-architecture-migration has interface type mismatches:\n- `data` vs `docs` field naming\n- `limit` vs `itemsPerPage` pagination naming\n\nFix these and rebuild. Then start the server and test auth endpoints:\n- POST /api/v1/auth/register\n- POST /api/v1/auth/login\n- GET /api/v1/auth/profile\n\nStart immediately.","label":"DTLX API Test","runtime":"subagent","agentId":"master-orchestrator","mode":"run"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":235,"output":507,"cacheRead":119777,"cacheWrite":299,"totalTokens":120818,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776134729309,"responseId":"062cdd4bd66ddf1a1c63f1a2c3ac0943"}}
