{"type":"message","id":"a2cd23ec","parentId":"e9295020","timestamp":"2026-04-14T04:38:16.343Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The subagent got aborted after 14 minutes (the OpenClaw run timeout), then it got resumed by the system and tried to continue with TroLy model which failed again with 500 errors. Then it timed out again.\n\nThe issue is:\n1. The subagent has a hard timeout of ~14 minutes (built into the run mode)\n2. When it times out, the system tries to resume it automatically\n3. The resumed session tries to use TroLy again (the broken model)\n4. It fails with 500 errors\n\nThe root cause: The `run` mode has a ~14 minute timeout. When it expires, the system auto-resumes with whatever model the session was using (which could be TroLy due to session inheritance).\n\n\nI should work directly in the current session instead of spawning a subagent—that way I have more control over the timeout and can use the DEV model directly. Let me just ask the user what they'd prefer.","thinkingSignature":"06ced2fca9099ec64145f77c7cf27ea45b4e184c89e590e97681ce12fd586f18"},{"type":"text","text":"**Vấn đề:** Subagent bị giới hạn timeout ~14 phút. Sau khi timeout, nó auto-resume nhưng lại dùng `TroLy` → fail lại.\n\n**Tiến triển thực tế:** Subagent đã làm được đến bước \"test auth endpoints\" trước khi bị kill — nghĩa là **build đã pass**.\n\n**Giải pháp:** Orbis nên làm trực tiếp trong session này để tránh timeout. Lead đồng ý không?"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":749,"output":340,"cacheRead":136955,"cacheWrite":483,"totalTokens":138527,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776141485862,"responseId":"062cf7af54fd21cac055c751b8ae513c"}}
