{"type":"compaction","id":"dd202934","parentId":"faafba2d","timestamp":"2026-04-14T04:56:37.890Z","summary":"## Goal\n1. Maintain the OpenClaw agent ecosystem with healthy pipelines\n2. Test API module auth on ahv-dtlx-backend (DTLX BE + FE)\n3. Keep only DTLX group (-5168104492) active; stop other group sessions\n4. Fix TypeScript build errors on DTLX BE branch `feature/clean-architecture-migration`\n\n## Constraints & Preferences\n- Git Workflow: only enforced for **OpenClaw agents** (human dev khuong ninh excluded)\n- Git author format: `[Khuowgn]-{agent-name}` with email `khuowgn.agents@anno.io`\n- Only DTLX group (-5168104492) runs; QLHV group (-5163901258) and AHV Works group (-5212380728) stopped\n- Do NOT use TroLy model — causes `providerSpecificData` 500 errors\n- Use `AHV-Holding-DEV` model for agent tasks\n\n## Progress\n### Done\n- [x] Updated Git Workflow: branch-per-task → lint → build → test → MR → Lead review\n- [x] Enforced Git Workflow in `senior-backend/DEV_GATE.md`, `senior-frontend/DEV_GATE.md`, `master-orchestrator/DEV_GATE.md`\n- [x] Created `master-orchestrator/docs/GIT_WORKFLOW.md`\n- [x] Commits: `a54a003` fix lint errors in BE (require→import, let→const)\n- [x] Set git author identity `[Khuowgn]-{agent}` for all workspaces and project repos\n- [x] QLHV group (-5163901258): stopped\n- [x] AHV Works group (-5212380728): stopped\n- [x] DTLX group (-5168104492): restarted for API test task\n- [x] QLHV MRs: all merged (!6 !7 !8 !9)\n- [x] DTLX-BE MR !166: `feature/clean-architecture-migration → refactor/main`, mergeable, pipeline ✅ success\n\n### In Progress\n- [ ] DTLX BE API test: subagent timed out (14m 9s) while examining TS error files\n- [ ] Fix 35+ TypeScript errors on `feature/clean-architecture-migration` branch (interface mismatches: `data` vs `docs`, `limit` vs `itemsPerPage`)\n\n### Blocked\n- DTLX BE build fails with TS errors on `feature/clean-architecture-migration` — interface type mismatches need manual fix\n- Gateway has 2 openclaw-gateway processes (zombie accumulation) — cannot kill without killing own session; needs manual server-side cleanup: `pkill -9 openclaw-gateway && pkill -9 -f confluence-mcp && openclaw gateway start`\n\n## Key Decisions\n- **Git Workflow enforced for agents only**: Lead said \"các agent thôi\" — human dev khuong ninh not affected\n- **DTLX group kept alive**: Lead corrected — it must stay running for API test task\n- **Git author identity per-agent**: `[Khuowgn]-senior-backend`, `[Khuowgn]-master-orchestrator` etc. with `@anno.io` domain\n- **No TroLy model**: causes `providerSpecificData` 500 errors; use `AHV-Holding-DEV`\n\n## Next Steps\n1. Fix DTLX BE TypeScript errors on `feature/clean-architecture-migration` branch — interface mismatches (`data`/`docs`, `limit`/`itemsPerPage`)\n2. Build + start BE server, test API auth endpoints: `POST /api/v1/auth/register`, `POST /api/v1/auth/login`, `GET /api/v1/auth/profile`\n3. Clean up zombie gateway processes (requires manual server command)\n4. MR !166 on DTLX-BE still pending Lead merge\n\n## Critical Context\n- **DTLX BE GitLab**: project ID `77055841`, `ahv-dtlx/ahv-dtlx-backend`\n- **DTLX FE GitLab**: project ID `77055851`, `ahv-dtlx/ahv-dtlx-frontend`\n- **QLHV BE GitLab**: project ID `81078323` (all MRs merged)\n- **QLHV FE GitLab**: project ID `81078350` (all MRs merged)\n- **GitLab token**: `glpat-c_N4qQVxbcktRro-S5rdwGM6MQpvOjEKdTpoZDBsYg8.01.170axqn65`\n- **Last BE lint fix commit**: `a54a003` on `fix/ci-git-pull-ff-only` branch (QLHV-BE)\n- **Active cron sessions**: `cron:ed2d0b5d` (QLHV 5p), `cron:6f3323ef` (DTLX 5p), `cron:e7885813` (Agent Status)\n- **HEARTBEAT.md location**: `/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/master-orchestrator/HEARTBEAT.md`\n- **MEMORY.md location**: `/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/master-orchestrator/MEMORY.md`\n- **MEMORY updated**: `heartbeat-state.json` at `/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/master-orchestrator/memory/heartbeat-state.json`\n\n---\n\n**Turn Context (split turn):**\n\n## Summary\n\n**Original Request:** User (Khương Nịnh) asks \"chạy đến đâu rồi\" — checking on task progress.\n\n**Early Progress:**\n- Identified that subagent `cd3256cb` using **TroLy model** (`AHV-Holding-TroLy`) is returning repeated 500 errors: `Cannot read properties of undefined (reading 'providerSpecificData')`\n- The DTLX group session (-5168104492) ended with errors at ~03:02 UTC\n- All `senior-backend` subagents are failing with the same TroLy model error\n- Located `/root/.openclaw/agents/senior-backend/agent/models.json` — both TroLy and DEV models are available\n- Confirmed via `grep` that `senior-backend` sessions are hardcoded to use `AHV-Holding-TroLy`\n\n**Context for Suffix:**\nThe assistant was in the middle of investigating where the default model is configured (checking `openclaw.json` for agent config overrides) in order to propose a fix — changing the default from TroLy to DEV model to resolve the 500 errors blocking all backend subagents.\n\n<read-files>\n/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/master-orchestrator/skills/master-orchestrator/SKILL.md\n</read-files>\n\n<modified-files>\n/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/master-orchestrator/DEV_GATE.md\n/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/master-orchestrator/MEMORY.md\n/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/master-orchestrator/docs/GIT_WORKFLOW.md\n/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/master-orchestrator/memory/heartbeat-state.json\n/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/senior-backend/DEV_GATE.md\n/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/senior-frontend/DEV_GATE.md\n</modified-files>","firstKeptEntryId":"544ed2ac","tokensBefore":156302,"details":{"readFiles":["/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/master-orchestrator/skills/master-orchestrator/SKILL.md"],"modifiedFiles":["/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/master-orchestrator/DEV_GATE.md","/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/master-orchestrator/MEMORY.md","/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/master-orchestrator/docs/GIT_WORKFLOW.md","/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/master-orchestrator/memory/heartbeat-state.json","/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/senior-backend/DEV_GATE.md","/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/senior-frontend/DEV_GATE.md"]},"fromHook":false}
