{"type":"message","id":"f9494dd3","parentId":"607eaa01","timestamp":"2026-04-14T05:00:43.472Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Lead wants comprehensive API testing - every endpoint in every module, AND seed data to test with. This is a big task. Let me spawn a subagent to do this comprehensively.","thinkingSignature":"4855cc68ebdd025a847c578efacb9a520607c0a0e23b0343cee4192757a0ed25"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_iajek7wqlpsq_1","name":"sessions_spawn","arguments":{"task":"You are the DTLX BE API Tester. Your job: test EVERY endpoint in EVERY module, seed data, and verify pipelines work.\n\n## Context\n- Backend running at http://localhost:3001\n- Auth: POST /api/v1/auth/signin with {\"username\":\"admin2\",\"password\":\"Admin123!\"} → accessToken\n- JWT bug already fixed (doc._id)\n- DB: ahv_dtlx (MongoDB)\n\n## PHASE 1: Map ALL routes\nRead these files to get every endpoint:\n- /root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/ahv-dtlx-backend/src/router.ts\n- /root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/ahv-dtlx-backend/src/routes/v1/education.routes.ts\n- /root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/ahv-dtlx-backend/src/routes/v1/operation.routes.ts\n- /root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/ahv-dtlx-backend/src/routes/v1/notification.routes.ts\n- /root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/ahv-dtlx-backend/src/routes/v1/system.routes.ts\n- /root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/ahv-dtlx-backend/src/modules/*/*.route.ts (all modules)\n\nBuild a complete list of ALL endpoints with their HTTP methods.\n\n## PHASE 2: Seed Data\nUse MongoDB CLI or mongosh to insert seed data into these collections:\n- users (at least 2 users)\n- courses (2-3 courses)\n- students  \n- payments (with received_fee field)\n- vehicles\n- stadiums\n- lessons\n- exams\n\nUse realistic Vietnamese data. Check existing schema from the service files to match fields correctly.\n\n## PHASE 3: Test ALL endpoints\nFor each endpoint found in Phase 1:\n1. Login to get fresh token\n2. Call the endpoint with appropriate params\n3. Record: HTTP status, response data, any errors\n4. Test edge cases (pagination, filters, sort)\n\n## PHASE 4: Test Aggregate Pipelines\nSpecifically test:\n- GET /dashboards/reports/revenues (with date filters)\n- GET /dashboards/reports/expenses (with date filters)  \n- GET /dashboards/reports/profits (should now work with data)\n- Any payment aggregation endpoints\n- Any revenue/cost aggregation in other modules\n\n## Output Format\nCreate a detailed report with:\n```\n## Module: [name]\n### Endpoint: METHOD /path\n- Status: 200/404/500/etc\n- Response: {summary of data}\n- Issues: [any problems]\n```\n\nSave report to: /root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/master-orchestrator/memory/2026-04-14-dtlx-api-test.md\n\n## Rules\n- Use AHV-Holding-DEV model\n- Be thorough - test every single endpoint\n- Log what you do as you go\n- If endpoint needs specific data format, check the service/validation files first","label":"DTLX Full API Test + Seed","runtime":"subagent","agentId":"master-orchestrator","model":"ahvholding/AHV-Holding-DEV","mode":"run"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":161,"output":790,"cacheRead":47540,"cacheWrite":2430,"totalTokens":50921,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776142825304,"responseId":"062cfceaa3c31dbc319f9e3c60e3ba6f"}}
