{"type":"message","id":"d8a2b83d","parentId":"bc689473","timestamp":"2026-04-14T06:55:56.853Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The issue is clear now:1. The admin2 user I created doesn't have the correct ROLE assigned. The user has no role, so `checkPermissions` middleware is blocking most endpoints.\n2. The `/users` endpoint also requires auth (403) - but I need to assign a role to admin2.\n\nLooking at the middleware: `checkPermissions` checks if the user has a role. I need to:1. Create a role (admin role)\n2. Assign the role to admin2 in `userroles` collection\n\nLet me check the userroles collection and create the proper assignment.","thinkingSignature":"39ee36ae08c78265866858ae4ea16852fbea325a746be44bc93a9a090361e3ce"},{"type":"text","text":"Vấn đề: admin2 không có **role** → bị `checkPermissions` chặn hết. Orbis fix ngay:\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_czu01ppeviih_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"mongosh \"mongodb://localhost:27017/dtlx\" --quiet --eval \"\n// Check existing roles\nprint('Roles:');\nprintjson(db.roles.find().toArray());\nprint('Userroles:');\nprintjson(db.userroles.find().toArray());\nprint('Users:');\nprintjson(db.users.find().toArray());\n\" 2>/dev/null","timeout":10}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":897,"output":263,"cacheRead":65717,"cacheWrite":2247,"totalTokens":69124,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776149748006,"responseId":"062d17f519d3b972d2466fee39b52597"}}
