{"type":"message","id":"b9a36b57","parentId":"9a513f98","timestamp":"2026-04-14T07:13:28.504Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Great progress! Both bugs are fixed:\n1. `/notify-users/unread/count` → 200 ✅\n2. `/reports/profits` → 200 ✅ (returns data with `revenue`, `expense`, `profits`, `arData`)\n\nThe JSON decode error is because the `/reports/profits` response body is too long and got truncated. But the important thing is both 500 bugs are fixed!\n\nLet me now fix the seeding issues. The login 500 error is actually from the `/reports/profits` endpoint returning a very long response that gets truncated during parsing. Let me just test the seed data more carefully.\n\n\nThe login call worked fine, so the error happened when I tried to seed student information—the `/reports/profits` response was truncated during the JSON parsing, which caused the urllib error handler to fail when trying to read the error body.\n\nLet me isolate the seed test to focus on fixing just the student and payment issues.","thinkingSignature":"7877e4bcc31fc859074e3468cee77ea594e3a901ec0f5204db17eb8d17bcef23"},{"type":"text","text":"**Cả 2 bugs 500 đã fix ✅** — `/notify-users/unread/count` và `/reports/profits` đều trả về 200! Giờ fix seed:\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_yx0by780t5wy_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"python3 << 'PYEOF'\nimport json, urllib.request, urllib.error\n\nBASE = \"http://localhost:3001/api/v1\"\ndef api(method, path, token=None, data=None):\n    url = f\"{BASE}{path}\"\n    headers = {\"Content-Type\":\"application/json\"}\n    if token: headers[\"Authorization\"] = f\"Bearer {token}\"\n    body = json.dumps(data).encode() if data else None\n    req = urllib.request.Request(url, data=body, headers=headers, method=method)\n    try:\n        resp = urllib.request.urlopen(req, timeout=20)\n        return resp.status, json.loads(resp.read())\n    except urllib.error.HTTPError as e:\n        body = e.read().decode()[:500]\n        return e.code, json.loads(body) if body.startswith('{') else body\n\n_, resp = api(\"POST\", \"/auth/signin\", None, {\"username\":\"admin2\",\"password\":\"Password123@\"})\ntoken = resp[\"data\"][\"accessToken\"]\nprint(\"✅ Login OK\")\n\n# Seed student-infos (needs received_fee and status)\ns, r = api(\"POST\", \"/student-infos\", token, {\n    \"username\":\"hv001\",\"password\":\"Pass123@\",\"email\":\"hv001@gmail.com\",\n    \"phone\":\"0912345001\",\"identity_card\":\"123456001\",\n    \"received_fee\":15000000,\"status\":\"studying\"\n})\nprint(f\"StudentInfos: {s} | {str(r)[:150]}\")\n\n# Seed license-category\ns, r = api(\"POST\", \"/license-categories\", token, {\"name\":\"Hạng B2\",\"code\":\"B2\"})\nprint(f\"LicenseCat: {s} | {str(r)[:150]}\")\n\n# Seed lead-sources\ns, r = api(\"POST\", \"/lead-sources\", token, {\"name\":\"Google Ads\"})\nprint(f\"LeadSources: {s} | {str(r)[:150]}\")\n\n# Seed lead-infos\ns, r = api(\"POST\", \"/lead-infos\", token, {\"name\":\"Khách hàng test\",\"phone\":\"0909000001\",\"source\":\"Google Ads\"})\nprint(f\"LeadInfos: {s} | {str(r)[:150]}\")\n\n# Seed guest leads\ns, r = api(\"POST\", \"/guests/leads\", token, {\"name\":\"Khách vãng lai\",\"phone\":\"0909000002\"})\nprint(f\"GuestLead: {s} | {str(r)[:150]}\")\n\n# Seed internal cost type then cost\ns, r = api(\"POST\", \"/internal-cost-types\", token, {\"name\":\"Chi phí xăng\"})\nict_id = r.get(\"data\",{}).get(\"doc\",{}).get(\"id\") if s in (200,201) else None\nprint(f\"ICT: {s} | id={ict_id}\")\nif ict_id:\n    s, r = api(\"POST\", \"/internal-costs\", token, {\n        \"internal_cost_type_id\":ict_id,\"amount\":500000,\n        \"description\":\"Chi phí xăng tháng 4\",\"payment_date\":\"2026-04-05\"\n    })\n    print(f\"InternalCost: {s} | {str(r)[:150]}\")\n\n# Seed student comment\ns, r = api(\"POST\", \"/student-comments\", token, {\n    \"student_id\":\"69dde49db5c07c63bb44ba89\",\n    \"comment\":\"Học viên chăm chỉ, tiến bộ nhanh\",\n    \"rating\":5\n})\nprint(f\"StudentComment: {s} | {str(r)[:150]}\")\nPYEOF","timeout":30}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":710,"output":1051,"cacheRead":110949,"cacheWrite":1281,"totalTokens":113991,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776150786609,"responseId":"062d1c04cfa0e47d7af67bf8d35e81bb"}}
