{"type":"message","id":"885491f4","parentId":"dce704b7","timestamp":"2026-04-14T07:14:30.701Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The problem is the StudentInfos POST is returning a 500 error, and the body is very long (truncated at 500 chars), causing JSON parse failure. This crashes the whole script.\n\nThe server is crashing on the StudentInfos POST. This could be a bug in the service. Let me test each one separately to find which one causes the 500.","thinkingSignature":"0880d88d042f04b34abac56f8f76911743978896a74d8a7c235dfcc9865dbf87"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_ibw0atxwunzo_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"curl -s http://localhost:3001/api/v1/auth/signin -X POST -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" -d '{\"username\":\"admin2\",\"password\":\"Password123@\"}' > /tmp/tok.txt && TOKEN=$(python3 -c \"import json; print(json.load(open('/tmp/tok.txt'))['data']['accessToken'])\")\n\n# Test each separately\nfor test in \"LicenseCat\" \"LeadSources\" \"GuestLead\"; do\n    case $test in\n        LicenseCat) DATA='{\"name\":\"B2\",\"code\":\"B2\"}'; PATH=\"/license-categories\" ;;\n        LeadSources) DATA='{\"name\":\"Google\"}'; PATH=\"/lead-sources\" ;;\n        GuestLead) DATA='{\"name\":\"Guest\",\"phone\":\"0909000002\"}'; PATH=\"/guests/leads\" ;;\n    esac\n    STATUS=$(curl -s -o /tmp/resp.txt -w \"%{http_code}\" -X POST \"http://localhost:3001/api/v1$PATH\" \\\n        -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" \\\n        -H \"Authorization: Bearer $TOKEN\" \\\n        -d \"$DATA\")\n    echo \"$test ($PATH): HTTP $STATUS | $(cat /tmp/resp.txt | head -c 100)\"\ndone","timeout":15}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":535,"output":378,"cacheRead":114640,"cacheWrite":1866,"totalTokens":117419,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776150859961,"responseId":"062d1c4def90a2214e0fafb7cb3