{"type":"message","id":"74fcbda2","parentId":"b8b506ec","timestamp":"2026-04-14T07:25:15.935Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Lead muốn test đầy đủ ~250 endpoints với data output chi tiết. Let me do a comprehensive test using Python, being very thorough. The issue is that many POST endpoints fail because of validation requirements. Let me focus on:\n\n1. GET endpoints - test all and show data structure\n2. For POST endpoints that need seed data, try to get the data right\n3. Show field names and data types\n\nLet me write a comprehensive script that:\n1. Logs in\n2. Tests all GET endpoints\n3. Shows field names and sample data for each\n4. Attempts POST with correct validation for each\n\nFirst, let me check how many actual endpoints there are by going through the route files more carefully.","thinkingSignature":"f7fefabeea42da47d00429b5f1f5d1284929609addbe4a8fcfce0660a8b74415"},{"type":"text","text":"Orbis test đầy đủ 250 endpoints chi tiết:\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_1w29mspgrgnq_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"find /root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/ahv-dtlx-backend/src/modules -name \"*.route.ts\" -exec grep -hE \"router\\.(get|post|put|patch|delete|options)\\(\" {} \\; 2>/dev/null | wc -l"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":0,"output":256,"cacheRead":5697,"cacheWrite":110392,"totalTokens":116345,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776151502871,"responseId":"062d1ed0fe8a870a21f27a24205bb66b"}}
