{"type":"compaction","id":"73e7dc85","parentId":"693d86ca","timestamp":"2026-04-14T07:32:18.604Z","summary":"## Goal\n1. Maintain the OpenClaw agent ecosystem with healthy pipelines\n2. Test API module auth on ahv-dtlx-backend (DTLX BE + FE) — comprehensive full API test\n3. Fix TypeScript build errors on DTLX BE branch `feature/clean-architecture-migration`\n4. Keep only DTLX group (-5168104492) active; stop other group sessions\n\n## Constraints & Preferences\n- Git Workflow: only enforced for **OpenClaw agents** (human dev khuong ninh excluded)\n- Git author format: `[Khuowgn]-{agent-name}` with email `khuowgn.agents@anno.io`\n- Only DTLX group (-5168104492) runs; QLHV group (-5163901258) and AHV Works group (-5212380728) stopped\n- **Do NOT use TroLy model** — causes `providerSpecificData` 500 errors; use `AHV-Holding-DEV`\n\n## Progress\n### Done\n- [x] **Root cause identified and fixed**: All `senior-backend` subagents were failing because `AHV-Holding-TroLy` model (default/first in models.json) returns 500 errors on every request\n- [x] **Reordered models.json** for all agents to put `AHV-Holding-DEV` first: senior-backend ✅, senior-frontend ✅, ui-ux-pro-max ✅, senior-devops ✅, senior-qa ✅, planner ✅\n- [x] **JWT bug identified and fixed**: `token.service.ts` line 17 had `doc.id` (undefined) instead of `doc._id` — Mongoose lean docs have `_id`, not `id`\n- [x] **Backend rebuilt** (`yarn build` — 59s) and **restarted** on port 3001\n- [x] **Admin user seeded**: Created admin2 user in MongoDB (`dtlx` database, collection `users`) with bcrypt hash for `Password123@`\n- [x] **Admin role assigned**: Created `admin` role in `roles` collection and `userroles` entry linking admin2 to admin role (required for `checkPermissions` middleware)\n- [x] **DTLX BE Start & Test subagent** completed successfully (5m51s) — server running port 3001, signin works, guest list works\n- [x] **Auth endpoints tested**: `POST /auth/signin` ✅ 200, `GET /guests` ✅ 200; `POST /auth/register` ❌ 404 (doesn't exist), `GET /auth/profile` ❌ 404 (doesn't exist)\n- [x] **JWT bug confirmed fixed**: Login returns valid token with `id` field in JWT payload\n- [x] **Comprehensive full API test completed** (60 endpoints via Python script): 40 endpoints 200 OK, 19 return 400 (validation), 2 return 500 (bugs), 8 return 404 (routes not mounted)\n- [x] **Pipeline aggregate testing**: `GET /reports/expenses` ✅ 200 (empty), `GET /reports/revenues` ✅ 200 (empty), `GET /reports/profits` ❌ 500 (bug)\n- [x] **Subagent timeouts handled**: 3 subagent attempts failed/timed out; switched to direct Python execution for reliability\n- [x] **DTLX BE build confirmed passing** (dist/ folder compiled successfully)\n- [x] QLHV group (-5163901258): stopped\n- [x] AHV Works group (-5212380728): stopped\n- [x] QLHV MRs: all merged (!6 !7 !8 !9)\n- [x] DTLX-BE MR !166: `feature/clean-architecture-migration → refactor/main`, mergeable, pipeline ✅ success\n\n### In Progress\n- [ ] **Fix remaining bugs**:\n  - `/reports/profits` → 500 error: `Cannot read properties of undefined (reading 'total_received_fee')` in payments service aggregate pipeline\n  - `/notify-users/unread/count` → 500 error\n- [ ] **Fix unmounted routes** (8 endpoints returning 404):\n  - `GET /teacher-infos` — route not mounted in router\n  - `POST /lessons` — route not mounted\n  - `GET /exam-results/me` — route not mounted\n  - `PATCH /exam-schedules` — route doesn't match\n  - `GET /conventions` — not mounted\n  - `GET /imports` — not mounted\n  - `POST /lead-sources` — validation error\n  - `POST /lead-infos` — validation error\n- [ ] **Seed data for full testing**: Many POST endpoints fail 400 due to missing/incorrect required fields in validation (e.g., `payment` needs `course_student_id`, `stadium.locate` needs URL format, `vehicle` needs `license_category_id`)\n\n### Blocked\n- DTLX BE build had TypeScript errors on `feature/clean-architecture-migration` — interface mismatches (`data`/`docs`, `limit`/`itemsPerPage`) — subagent got past this; TS build now passes ✅\n- Gateway zombie processes (2 openclaw-gateway processes) — cannot kill without killing own session; needs manual server-side cleanup\n\n## Key Decisions\n- **Python over subagent for API testing**: 3 subagents failed due to model API timeouts and mongosh unavailability in sandbox; switched to direct Python execution for reliable comprehensive testing\n- **DEV model as default for all agents**: Reordered models.json for 6 agents to make `AHV-Holding-DEV` the first entry (agent's default = first model in list)\n- **DTLX group kept alive**: Lead confirmed it should stay running for API test task\n- **MongoDB database name**: DTLX backend uses `dtlx` database (not `ahv_dtlx`) — confirmed via `mongosh`\n- **Admin seeding via mongosh**: Used `mongosh` directly to insert admin2 user with bcrypt hash and assign admin role since there's no registration endpoint and all user creation requires auth\n\n## Next Steps\n1. **Fix `/reports/profits` 500 bug**: Investigate `total_received_fee` undefined in payments service aggregate — likely `docTotalFee[0]` is undefined or field name mismatch in the `$group` stage of the profits calculation pipeline\n2. **Fix `/notify-users/unread/count` 500 bug**: Check notify-users controller/service\n3. **Seed test data properly**: Use correct validation field names to seed courses, vehicles (need `license_category_id`), students, payments (need `course_student_id`), stadiums (locate must be URL), etc.\n4. **Test aggregate pipelines with data**: After seeding payments and internal costs, verify `revenues`, `expenses`, and `profits` aggregates return correct calculated totals\n5. **MR !166 on DTLX-BE**: Still pending Lead merge\n6. **Clean up zombie gateway processes** (requires manual server command)\n\n## Critical Context\n- **DTLX BE GitLab**: project ID `77055841`, `ahv-dtlx/ahv-dtlx-backend`\n- **DTLX FE GitLab**: project ID `77055851`, `ahv-dtlx/ahv-dtlx-frontend`\n- **Backend running**: `http://localhost:3001` (port 3001), server started via `node dist/server.js`\n- **MongoDB**: `mongodb://localhost:27017/dtlx` (database `dtlx`), Docker container `mongo:4.4`, port 27017\n- **Login credentials**: `admin2` / `Password123@` (password hash: `$2a$10$lPWHnKGf2GBD9Yp51eiq6eP0w2Nh0VSfAftWctHBCo2qdqKtotM0q`)\n- **Admin role ID**: `69dde52739a2d248bd44ba89` (in `roles` collection)\n- **JWT fix file**: `/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/ahv-dtlx-backend/src/modules/auth/token.service.ts` line 17 — `doc.id` → `doc._id`\n- **HEARTBEAT.md location**: `/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/master-orchestrator/HEARTBEAT.md`\n- **MEMORY.md location**: `/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/master-orchestrator/MEMORY.md`\n- **API test report**: `/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/master-orchestrator/memory/2026-04-14-dtlx-api-test.md`\n- **GitLab token**: `glpat-c_N4qQVxbcktRro-S5rdwGM6MQpvOjEKdTpoZDBsYg8.01.170axqn65`\n- **Active cron sessions**: `cron:ed2d0b5d` (stale/QLHV), `cron:6f3323ef` (DTLX 5p), `cron:e7885813` (Agent Status — reporting stale data)\n\n---\n\n**Turn Context (split turn):**\n\n## Original Request\nUser asked to check if API endpoints return data and fix any issues (\"Xem có data trả về chưa sai đâu fix\").\n\n## Early Progress\n- Identified all endpoints via data check — only `/courses` and `/courses/all` had data (3 items), everything else was empty.\n- Found and confirmed 2 root causes of **500 errors**:\n  1. `/dashboards/reports/profits` — `coursesStudents.service.ts` line 774: `docTotalFee[0].total_received_fee` crashed when array was empty (no data seeded yet).\n  2. `/notify-users/unread/count` — `notifyUsers.controller.ts` used `String(req.query.user_id)` with no fallback, causing mongoose `ObjectId(\"undefined\")` crash.\n\n## Context for Suffix\nThe suffix begins after the build was rebuilt and server restarted, confirming both 500 fixes worked (both endpoints now return 200). The remaining work shown in the suffix is:\n- Investigating why certain POST endpoints return **400 validation errors** (LicenseCat, GuestLead) or **500 on transactions** (StudentInfos — MongoDB not a replica set, so transaction operations fail).\n- Testing seed data for `/license-categories`, `/guests/leads`, `/lead-sources` (LeadSources already works), and `/student-infos`.\n- The `/reports/profits` response body was very long, causing Python's `urllib` to truncate responses and trigger `JSONDecodeError` in the error handler — this was a test script artifact, not a server bug.\n\n<read-files>\n/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/master-orchestrator/skills/master-orchestrator/SKILL.md\n</read-files>\n\n<modified-files>\n/root/.openclaw/agents/senior-backend/agent/models.json\n/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/ahv-dtlx-backend/src/modules/notifyUsers/notifyUsers.controller.ts\n/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/master-orchestrator/DEV_GATE.md\n/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/master-orchestrator/MEMORY.md\n/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/master-orchestrator/docs/GIT_WORKFLOW.md\n/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/master-orchestrator/memory/heartbeat-state.json\n/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/senior-backend/DEV_GATE.md\n/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/senior-frontend/DEV_GATE.md\n/tmp/dtlx-final-test.py\n/tmp/dtlx-full-api-test.py\n/tmp/dtlx-full-test.py\n/tmp/dtlx-seed-test.py\n/tmp/start-dtlx-be.sh\n/tmp/start-dtlx.sh\n</modified-files>","firstKeptEntryId":"3255447e","tokensBefore":135888,"details":{"readFiles":["/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/master-orchestrator/skills/master-orchestrator/SKILL.md"],"modifiedFiles":["/root/.openclaw/agents/senior-backend/agent/models.json","/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/ahv-dtlx-backend/src/modules/notifyUsers/notifyUsers.controller.ts","/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/master-orchestrator/DEV_GATE.md","/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/master-orchestrator/MEMORY.md","/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/master-orchestrator/docs/GIT_WORKFLOW.md","/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/master-orchestrator/memory/heartbeat-state.json","/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/senior-backend/DEV_GATE.md","/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/senior-frontend/DEV_GATE.md","/tmp/dtlx-final-test.py","/tmp/dtlx-full-api-test.py","/tmp/dtlx-full-test.py","/tmp/dtlx-seed-test.py","/tmp/start-dtlx-be.sh","/tmp/start-dtlx.sh"]},"fromHook":false}
{"type":"message","id":"0ff5a72e","parentId":"73e7dc85","timestamp":"2026-04-14T07:32:23.216Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[Tue 2026-04-14 07:22 UTC] 🔴 Orbis Alert — 07:18 UTC 14 Apr\n\nLead direct session (6053576134) — FAILED\n• Reason: providerSpecificData 500 errors (TroLy model)\n• TroLy model: persistent API errors across 5+ subagents\n• No live user task — awaiting your input\n\nPipeline: DEGRADED\nActive sessions: 4 (3 crons + 1 group)\nBlockers: DTLX admin2 perms | TroLy model errors | mongosh/DB\n\n— Orbis 🌐"}],"timestamp":1776151943044,"provenance":{"kind":"inter_session","sourceSessionKey":"agent:master-orchestrator:cron:ed2d0b5d-fc56-42eb-a8fc-973a48024df7","sourceTool":"sessions_send"}}}
{"type":"message","id":"10ab6ba2","parentId":"0ff5a72e","timestamp":"2026-04-14T07:33:21.844Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The cron session is reporting a stale alert that I've already resolved. The TroLy model issue was fixed by reordering models.json. Let me update the cron session with the latest status and continue the API testing.\n\nActually, this appears to be a heartbeat/status message from a cron session. I should just continue with my work - the server is running and I'm testing endpoints. The alert from the cron is outdated (based on old session state). \n\nLet me continue the comprehensive API testing with the rebuilt+restarted server. Let me now do a comprehensive test of all endpoints.","thinkingSignature":"96add1281933318cc0e1144f445784210c49c823bfb6d7db3c2e71bec15d9405"},{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] Alert cũ từ cron — đã resolve rồi. Tiếp tục test:\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_1i5zrhavzwo1_1","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"/tmp/dtlx-full250.py","content":"#!/usr/bin/env python3\n\"\"\"DTLX BE — Full API Test: response structure + data shape\"\"\"\nimport json, urllib.request, urllib.error, time\n\nBASE = \"http://localhost:3001/api/v1\"\n\ndef api(method, path, token=None, data=None):\n    url = BASE + path\n    headers = {\"Content-Type\":\"application/json\"}\n    if token: headers[\"Authorization\"] = f\"Bearer {token}\"\n    body = json.dumps(data).encode() if data else None\n    req = urllib.request.Request(url, data=body, headers=headers, method=method)\n    try:\n        resp = urllib.request.urlopen(req, timeout=20)\n        return resp.status, json.loads(resp.read())\n    except urllib.error.HTTPError as e:\n        return e.code, e.read()[:400].decode(\"utf-8\", errors=\"replace\")\n    except Exception as e:\n        return 0, str(e)[:80]\n\n_, r = api(\"POST\", \"/auth/signin\", None, {\"username\":\"admin2\",\"password\":\"Password123@\"})\ntoken = r[\"data\"][\"accessToken\"]\n\ndef get_id(path):\n    s, r = api(\"GET\", path, token)\n    if s == 200:\n        for k in [\"docs\",\"result\",\"data\"]:\n            d = r.get(k, r) if isinstance(r,dict) else {}\n            docs = d if isinstance(d, list) else d.get(k, [])\n            if docs and len(docs) > 0:\n                return docs[0].get(\"id\") or docs[0].get(\"_id\")\n    return None\n\ndef sample_fields(docs):\n    if not docs: return []\n    first = docs[0] if isinstance(docs, list) else docs\n    skip = {\"_id\",\"createdAt\",\"updatedAt\",\"__v\"}\n    return [k for k in first.keys() if k not in skip]\n\ndef fmt_val(v):\n    if isinstance(v, (dict, list)): return f\"<{type(v).__name__}>\"\n    if isinstance(v, str) and len(v) > 35: return v[:35]+\"…\"\n    return repr(v)\n\n# ─── TEST ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────\nRESULTS = []\nOK, ERR, WARN = 0, 0, 0\n\ndef test(method, path, body=None, need_auth=True, desc=\"\"):\n    global OK, ERR, WARN\n    t = token if need_auth else None\n    s, r = api(method, path, t, body)\n    icon = \"✅\" if s in (200,201) else (\"⚠️\" if s in (400,404) else \"❌\")\n    if s in (200,201): OK += 1\n    elif s in (400,404): WARN += 1\n    else: ERR += 1\n\n    d = r.get(\"data\", r) if isinstance(r, dict) else {}\n    docs = d.get(\"docs\", d.get(\"result\", d.get(\"data\",[])))\n    if isinstance(docs, list) and len(docs) > 0:\n        fields = sample_fields(docs)\n        RESULTS.append(f\"{icon} [{s}] {method:6} {path:50} | {len(docs)} items | {fields}\")\n        print(f\"{icon} [{s}] {method:6} {path}\")\n        print(f\"      items={len(docs)} | fields={fields}\")\n        if docs:\n            first = docs[0]\n            for k,v in list(first.items())[:5]:\n                if k not in (\"_id\",\"createdAt\",\"updatedAt\",\"__v\"):\n                    print(f\"      {k} = {fmt_val(v)}\")\n    elif isinstance(d, dict) and d:\n        fields = [k for k in d.keys() if k not in (\"_id\",\"createdAt\",\"updatedAt\",\"__v\")]\n        RESULTS.append(f\"{icon} [{s}] {method:6} {path:50} | keys={fields}\")\n        print(f\"{icon} [{s}] {method:6} {path}\")\n        print(f\"      keys={fields}\")\n        for k,v in list(d.items())[:5]:\n            if k not in (\"_id\",\"createdAt\",\"updatedAt\",\"__v\"):\n                RESULTS[-1] += f\"\\n      {k}={fmt_val(v)}\"\n    else:\n        msg = r.get(\"message\",\"\") if isinstance(r,dict) else str(r)[:60]\n        RESULTS.append(f\"{icon} [{s}] {method:6} {path:50} | {msg[:60]}\")\n        print(f\"{icon} [{s}] {method:6} {path} | {msg[:60]}\")\n    print()\n    return s\n\n# Get IDs\nids = {}\nfor path, key in [(\"/courses\",\"cid\"),(\"/stadiums\",\"sid\"),(\"/roles\",\"rid\"),\n                   (\"/agents\",\"aid\"),(\"/users/role\",\"uid\"),(\"/users/teachers\",\"tid\"),\n                   (\"/lesson-types\",\"ltid\"),(\"/users/sales\",\"said\"),(\"/lead-sources\",\"lsid\")]:\n    ids[key] = get_id(path)\n\nprint(f\"IDs: {ids}\\n{'='*70}\\n\")\n\n# AUTH\nprint(\"── AUTH ──\")\ntest(\"POST\",\"/auth/signin\",{\"username\":\"admin2\",\"password\":\"Password123@\"},False)\ntest(\"PATCH\",\"/auth/change-password\",{\"oldPassword\":\"Password123@\",\"newPassword\":\"Password123@\"})\ntest(\"POST\",\"/auth/refetch-token\")\n\n# GUESTS\nprint(\"── GUESTS ──\")\ntest(\"GET\",\"/guests\",None,False)\ntest(\"GET\",\"/guests/:id\",None,False)  # bad id → 400\n\n# ROLES + AGENTS + USERS\nprint(\"── SYSTEM ──\")\ntest(\"GET\",\"/roles\")\ntest(\"GET\",\"/agents\")\ntest(\"GET\",\"/users/role\")\ntest(\"GET\",\"/user-role\")\ntest(\"GET\",\"/log-tasks\")\ntest(\"GET\",\"/devices\")\n\n# LICENSE CATEGORIES\nprint(\"── LICENSE CATEGORIES ──\")\ntest(\"GET\",\"/license-categories\")\n\n# COURSES\nprint(\"── COURSES ──\")\ntest(\"GET\",\"/courses\")\ntest(\"GET\",\"/courses/all\")\ntest(\"GET\",\"/courses/:id\".replace(\":id\", ids.get(\"cid\",\"\")))\ntest(\"GET\",\"/courses/student/:studentId\".replace(\":studentId\", ids.get(\"uid\",\"\")))\ntest(\"GET\",\"/courses-students\")\ntest(\"GET\",\"/courses-students/filter\")\ntest(\"GET\",\"/courses-students/labels\")\n\n# EDUCATION\nprint(\"── EDUCATION ──\")\ntest(\"GET\",\"/lessons\")\ntest(\"GET\",\"/lessons/detail-by-date\")\ntest(\"GET\",\"/lessons/course-student/:csid\".replace(\":csid\", ids.get(\"csid\",\"none\")))\ntest(\"GET\",\"/lesson-types\")\ntest(\"GET\",\"/lesson-types/filter\")\ntest(\"GET\",\"/lesson-types/:id\".replace(\":id\", ids.get(\"ltid\",\"\")))\ntest(\"GET\",\"/teacher-infos\")\ntest(\"GET\",\"/teacher-infos/ranking\")\ntest(\"GET\",\"/teacher-infos/user/:uid\".replace(\":uid\", ids.get(\"uid\",\"\")))\ntest(\"GET\",\"/student-infos\")\ntest(\"GET\",\"/student-infos/all\")\ntest(\"GET\",\"/exams\")\ntest(\"GET\",\"/exams/detail\")\ntest(\"GET\",\"/exams/check-status-graduate\")\ntest(\"GET\",\"/exam-results\")\ntest(\"GET\",\"/exam-results/me\")\ntest(\"GET\",\"/exam-schedules\")\ntest(\"GET\",\"/exam-schedules/:id\".replace(\":id\", ids.get(\"esid\",\"\")))\ntest(\"GET\",\"/exam-registrations\")\ntest(\"GET\",\"/exam-registrations/me\")\ntest(\"GET\",\"/work-calendars\")\ntest(\"GET\",\"/work-calendars/users/:uid\".replace(\":uid\", ids.get(\"uid\",\"\")))\n\n# OPERATIONS\nprint(\"── OPERATIONS ──\")\ntest(\"GET\",\"/vehicles\")\ntest(\"GET\",\"/vehicles/:id/total-time\".replace(\":id\", ids.get(\"cid\",\"\")))\ntest(\"GET\",\"/stadiums\")\ntest(\"GET\",\"/stadiums/:id\".replace(\":id\", ids.get(\"sid\",\"\")))\ntest(\"GET\",\"/payments\")\ntest(\"GET\",\"/payments/total\")\ntest(\"GET\",\"/payments/course/:csid\".replace(\":csid\", ids.get(\"csid\",\"none\")))\ntest(\"GET\",\"/lead-sources\")\ntest(\"GET\",\"/lead-sources/:id\".replace(\":id\", ids.get(\"lsid\",\"\")))\ntest(\"GET\",\"/lead-infos\")\ntest(\"GET\",\"/internal-cost-types\")\ntest(\"GET\",\"/internal-costs/vehicle\")\ntest(\"GET\",\"/internal-costs/office\")\ntest(\"GET\",\"/internal-costs/vehicle/total\")\ntest(\"GET\",\"/internal-costs/office/total\")\n\n# DASHBOARD\nprint(\"── DASHBOARD ──\")\ntest(\"GET\",\"/dashboards/reports/expenses\")\ntest(\"GET\",\"/dashboards/reports/revenues\")\ntest(\"GET\",\"/dashboards/reports/profits\")\n\n# NOTIFICATIONS\nprint(\"── NOTIFICATIONS ──\")\ntest(\"GET\",\"/notify-configs\")\ntest(\"GET\",\"/notify-contents\")\ntest(\"GET\",\"/notify-users/unread/count\")\ntest(\"GET\",\"/notifies\")\ntest(\"GET\",\"/notifies/schedules\")\ntest(\"GET\",\"/notifies/mobile\")\n\n# COMMENTS\nprint(\"── COMMENTS ──\")\ntest(\"GET\",\"/student-comments\")\ntest(\"GET\",\"/teacher-comments\")\n\n# USERS sub-routes\nprint(\"── USERS/TEACHER ──\")\ntest(\"GET\",\"/users/teachers\")\ntest(\"GET\",\"/users/teachers/:id\".replace(\":id\", ids.get(\"tid\",\"\")))\ntest(\"GET\",\"/users/teachers/:id/students\".replace(\":id\", ids.get(\"tid\",\"\")))\ntest(\"GET\",\"/users/teachers/:id/lessons\".replace(\":id\", ids.get(\"tid\",\"\")))\ntest(\"GET\",\"/users/teachers/:id/lessons/detail\".replace(\":id\", ids.get(\"tid\",\"\")))\ntest(\"GET\",\"/users/teachers/:id/work-time\".replace(\":id\", ids.get(\"tid\",\"\")))\n\nprint(\"── USERS/SALES ──\")\ntest(\"GET\",\"/users/sales\")\ntest(\"GET\",\"/users/sales/counter\")\ntest(\"GET\",\"/users/sales/:id/info\".replace(\":id\", ids.get(\"said\",\"\")))\n\nprint(\"── USERS/STUDENT ──\")\ntest(\"GET\",\"/users/students\")\ntest(\"GET\",\"/users/students/:id\".replace(\":id\", ids.get(\"uid\",\"\")))\ntest(\"GET\",\"/users/students/:id/lessons\".replace(\":id\", ids.get(\"uid\",\"\")))\ntest(\"GET\",\"/users/students/:id/lessons/detail\".replace(\":id\", ids.get(\"uid\",\"\")))\ntest(\"GET\",\"/users/students/:id/exams\".replace(\":id\", ids.get(\"uid\",\"\")))\ntest(\"GET\",\"/users/students/:id/exams/detail\".replace(\":id\", ids.get(\"uid\",\"\")))\n\n# TEACHER INFOS\nprint(\"── TEACHER INFOS ──\")\ntest(\"GET\",\"/teacher-infos\")\ntest(\"GET\",\"/teacher-infos/ranking\")\n\n# CONVENTIONS + IMPORTS\nprint(\"── CONVENTIONS / IMPORTS ──\")\ntest(\"GET\",\"/conventions\")\ntest(\"GET\",\"/imports\")\n\n# ─── POST CREATE ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────\nprint(\"── POST CREATE ──\")\ntest(\"POST\",\"/courses\",{\"code\":\"B2-2026-TEST\",\"course_fee\":15000000,\"status\":\"active\"})\ntest(\"POST\",\"/stadiums\",{\"name\":\"Sân Test 99\",\"locate\":\"https://maps.google.com/?q=11,107\"})\ntest(\"POST\",\"/lesson-types\",{\"name\":\"Lý thuyết 2\",\"vehicle_apply\":\"car\",\"status\":\"active\",\"is_practice\":False})\ntest(\"POST\",\"/internal-cost-types\",{\"name\":\"Chi phí mới\"})\ntest(\"POST\",\"/roles\",{\"role_name\":\"manager2\"})\ntest(\"POST\",\"/student-comments\",{\"comment\":\"Tốt\",\"rating\":5})\ntest(\"POST\",\"/teacher-comments\",{\"comment\":\"Giỏi\",\"rating\":5})\n\n# ─── PATCH UPDATE ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────\nprint(\"── PATCH UPDATE ──\")\ntest(\"PATCH\",\"/courses/{id}\".format(id=ids.get(\"cid\",\"\")),{\"description\":\"updated\"})\ntest(\"PATCH\",\"/stadiums/{id}\".format(id=ids.get(\"sid\",\"\")),{\"name\":\"Sân đổi tên\"})\ntest(\"PATCH\",\"/roles/{id}\".format(id=ids.get(\"rid\",\"\")),{\"role_name\":\"admin_renamed\"})\n\n# ─── SUMMARY ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────\nprint(\"=\"*70)\nprint(f\"RESULTS: ✅ {OK}  ⚠️ {WARN}  ❌ {ERR}  |  Total tested\")\nprint(\"=\"*70)\n\n# Save to file\nreport = \"\\n\".join(RESULTS)\nwith open(\"/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/master-orchestrator/memory/2026-04-14-dtlx-full-test.md\",\"w\") as f:\n    f.write(\"# DTLX BE — Full API Test 2026-04-14\\n\\n\")\n    f.write(f\"## Summary: ✅ {OK} ⚠️ {WARN} ❌ {ERR}\\n\\n\")\n    f.write(report)\nprint(\"Saved to memory/2026-04-14-dtlx-full-test.md\")\n"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":0,"output":3142,"cacheRead":13401,"cacheWrite":24759,"totalTokens":41302,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite