{"type":"message","id":"bbb0f8e9","parentId":"6c1f4b45","timestamp":"2026-04-14T07:33:55.896Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I see:\n1. `/courses` returns docs with `id` field\n2. `/stadiums` returns docs with `id` field\n3. `/roles` returns docs WITHOUT `id` or `_id` field! Just `role_name`. Bug confirmed.\n4. `/users/role` returns docs with `_id` but no `id` field. Need to use `_id`.\n5. `/users/teachers` returns 404\n6. `/users/sales` returns docs with empty keys\n\nThe roles collection has no `_id` field visible in the response - this might be because it's using a MongoDB view or the docs don't have _id. \n\nActually, wait - every MongoDB document has an `_id` by default, so the roles response is almost certainly a bug in the service layer, possibly using `.select()` to exclude the `_id` field. I need to check the roles service to confirm. Let me fix the test script to use the correct field names for each collection, then write a comprehensive test that handles all these variations.","thinkingSignature":"bc08c25ea1106ef2ddab5599e414e1355868769ee2eb0b1f564a28be2a9ddd24"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_rzbw2yuu7zks_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"python3 << 'PYEOF'\nimport json, urllib.request, urllib.error\n\nBASE = \"http://localhost:3001/api/v1\"\ndef api(m, p, t=None, b=None):\n    url = BASE+p; h={\"Content-Type\":\"application/json\"}\n    if t: h[\"Authorization\"]=f\"Bearer {t}\"\n    req = urllib.request.Request(url, data=json.dumps(b).encode() if b else None, headers=h, method=m)\n    try:\n        r=urllib.request.urlopen(req,timeout=15)\n        return r.status, json.loads(r.read())\n    except urllib.error.HTTPError as e:\n        return e.code, e.read()[:300].decode()\n    except Exception as e:\n        return 0, str(e)\n\n_, r = api(\"POST\",\"/auth/signin\",None,{\"username\":\"admin2\",\"password\":\"Password123@\"})\ntoken = r[\"data\"][\"accessToken\"]\n\n# Fix: roles uses _id, users/role uses _id\nfor path in [\"/roles\",\"/users/role\",\"/users/sales\",\"/teacher-infos\"]:\n    s, r = api(\"GET\", path, token)\n    d = r.get(\"data\", r) if isinstance(r, dict) else {}\n    docs = d.get(\"docs\", d.get(\"result\", []))\n    if docs:\n        print(f\"GET {path}\")\n        print(f\"  first doc: {json.dumps(docs[0], default=str)[:200]}\")\n        print(f\"  has _id: {'_id' in docs[0]}, has id: {'id' in docs[0]}\")\n    else:\n        print(f\"GET {path} -> status={s}, keys={list(d.keys())}\")\nPYEOF","timeout":20}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":642,"output":622,"cacheRead":41231,"cacheWrite":1543,"totalTokens":44038,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776152022857,"responseId":"062d20d7fe14120f2749af049b5ec559"}}
{"type":"message","id":"bff19249","parentId":"bbb0f8e9","timestamp":"2026-04-14T07:33:56.526Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_rzbw2yuu7zks_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"GET /roles\n  first doc: {\"role_name\": \"admin\"}\n  has _id: False, has id: False\nGET /users/role\n  first doc: {\"_id\": \"69dde49db5c07c63bb44ba89\", \"username\": \"admin2\", \"email\": \"admin2@gmail.com\", \"first_name\": \"system\", \"last_name\": \"admin2\", \"phone\": \"030000000001\", \"gender\": \"male\", \"status\": \"active\", \"do\n  has _id: True, has id: False\nGET /users/sales -> status=200, keys=['docs', 'meta']\nGET /teacher-infos -> status=404, keys=[]"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":448,"aggregated":"GET /roles\n  first doc: {\"role_name\": \"admin\"}\n  has _id: False, has id: False\nGET /users/role\n  first doc: {\"_id\": \"69dde49db5c07c63bb44ba89\", \"username\": \"admin2\", \"email\": \"admin2@gmail.com\", \"first_name\": \"system\", \"last_name\": \"admin2\", \"phone\": \"030000000001\", \"gender\": \"male\", \"status\": \"active\", \"do\n  has _id: True, has id: False\nGET /users/sales -> status=200, keys=['docs', 'meta']\nGET /teacher-infos -> status=404, keys=[]","cwd":"/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/master-orchestrator"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1776152036520}}
{"type":"message","id":"4d3b37e8","parentId":"bff19249","timestamp":"2026-04-14T07:34:40.616Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I can see:1. `/roles` - docs don't have `_id` or `id` - BUG in the service (`.select()` probably excludes _id)\n2. `/users/role` - uses `_id`\n3. `/users/sales` - returns empty docs (no sales users yet)4. `/teacher-infos` - 404 (teacher-infos not mounted)Now let me write the comprehensive test with all the correct IDs and field names. Let me focus on what's most useful for the Lead - actually verifying the response structure and data quality.","thinkingSignature":"38caee3aa3f3568cf65df105f0c615bb61a6dbc4ed6f47bd23fe3a8d0e6309e3"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_dnsznlabq9yj_1","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"/tmp/dtlx-full-test2.py","content":"#!/usr/bin/env python3\n\"\"\"DTLX BE — Comprehensive API Test v2\"\"\"\nimport json, urllib.request, urllib.error\n\nBASE = \"http://localhost:3001/api/v1\"\ndef api(m, p, t=None, b=None):\n    url = BASE+p; h={\"Content-Type\":\"application/json\"}\n    if t: h[\"Authorization\"]=f\"Bearer {t}\"\n    req = urllib.request.Request(url, data=json.dumps(b).encode() if b else None, headers=h, method=m)\n    try:\n        r=urllib.request.urlopen(req,timeout=20)\n        return r.status, json.loads(r.read())\n    except urllib.error.HTTPError as e:\n        return e.code, e.read()[:400].decode()\n    except Exception as e:\n        return 0, str(e)[:80]\n\n_, r = api(\"POST\",\"/auth/signin\",None,{\"username\":\"admin2\",\"password\":\"Password123@\"})\ntoken = r[\"data\"][\"accessToken\"]\n\ndef get_first_id(path):\n    s, r = api(\"GET\", path, token)\n    if s != 200: return None\n    d = r.get(\"data\", r)\n    docs = d if isinstance(d, list) else d.get(\"docs\", d.get(\"result\", []))\n    if not docs: return None\n    return docs[0].get(\"id\") or docs[0].get(\"_id\")\n\ndef test(m, p, body=None, t=None):\n    s, r = api(m, p, t or token, body)\n    icon = \"✅\" if s in (200,201) else (\"⚠️\" if s in (400,403,404) else \"❌\")\n    d = r.get(\"data\", r) if isinstance(r, dict) else {}\n    docs = d.get(\"docs\", d.get(\"result\", d.get(\"revenues\", d.get(\"data\", []))))\n    msg = \"\"\n    if isinstance(docs, list) and docs:\n        cnt = len(docs)\n        skip = {\"_id\",\"createdAt\",\"updatedAt\",\"created_at\",\"updated_at\",\"__v\"}\n        fields = [k for k in docs[0].keys() if k not in skip]\n        vals = {k:(v[:30]+\"…\" if isinstance(v,str) and len(v)>30 else v) for k,v in list(docs[0].items()) if k not in skip}\n        msg = f\"{icon} [{s:3}] {m:6} {p:48} | {cnt} items | {fields}\"\n        print(f\"{msg}\")\n        for k,v in list(vals.items())[:4]:\n            print(f\"       {k} = {repr(v)}\")\n    elif isinstance(d, dict) and d:\n        skip = {\"_id\",\"createdAt\",\"updatedAt\",\"created_at\",\"updated_at\",\"__v\"}\n        fields = [k for k in d.keys() if k not in skip]\n        vals = {k:(v[:30]+\"…\" if isinstance(v,str) and len(v)>30 else v) for k,v in list(d.items()) if k not in skip}\n        msg = f\"{icon} [{s:3}] {m:6} {p:48} | keys={fields}\"\n        print(f\"{msg}\")\n        for k,v in list(vals.items())[:6]:\n            print(f\"       {k} = {repr(v)}\")\n    else:\n        msg_raw = r.get(\"message\",\"\") if isinstance(r,dict) else str(r)[:60]\n        msg = f\"{icon} [{s:3}] {m:6} {p:48} | {msg_raw[:60]}\"\n        print(f\"{msg}\")\n    print()\n    return s\n\nOK, WARN, ERR = 0, 0, 0\n\ndef t(m, p, body=None):\n    global OK, WARN, ERR\n    s = test(m, p, body)\n    if s in (200,201): OK+=1\n    elif s in (400,403,404): WARN+=1\n    else: ERR+=1\n    return s\n\n# Pre-load IDs\ncid   = get_first_id(\"/courses\")\nsid   = get_first_id(\"/stadiums\")\nltid  = get_first_id(\"/lesson-types\")\neid   = get_first_id(\"/exams\")\nuid   = get_first_id(\"/users/role\")\naid   = get_first_id(\"/agents\")\ncsid  = None  # no courses-students data yet\nsaid  = get_first_id(\"/users/sales\")\nlsid  = get_first_id(\"/lead-sources\")\nesid  = None  # no exam-schedules data\n\nprint(f\"IDs: cid={cid}, sid={sid}, ltid={ltid}, eid={eid}, uid={uid}, aid={aid}, csid={csid}, said={said}, lsid={lsid}\")\nprint(\"=\"*80)\n\n# ── AUTH ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────\nprint(\"🔐 AUTH\")\nt(\"POST\",\"/auth/signin\",{\"username\":\"admin2\",\"password\":\"Password123@\"})\nt(\"PATCH\",\"/auth/change-password\",{\"oldPassword\":\"X\",\"newPassword\":\"Y\"})\nt(\"POST\",\"/auth/refetch-token\")\n\n# ── GUEST ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────\nprint(\"👤 GUEST\")\nt(\"GET\",\"/guests\",None,False)\nt(\"GET\",\"/guests\",None,True)  # with auth\n\n# ── SYSTEM ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────\nprint(\"⚙️ SYSTEM\")\nt(\"GET\",\"/roles\")\nt(\"GET\",\"/agents\")\nt(\"GET\",\"/users/role\")\nt(\"GET\",\"/user-role\")\nt(\"GET\",\"/log-tasks\")\nt(\"GET\",\"/devices\")\n\n# ── LICENSE CATEGORIES ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────\nprint(\"📋 LICENSE CATEGORIES\")\nt(\"GET\",\"/license-categories\")\n\n# ── COURSES ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────\nprint(\"📚 COURSES\")\nt(\"GET\",\"/courses\")\nt(\"GET\",\"/courses/all\")\nif cid: t(\"GET\",f\"/courses/{cid}\")\nt(\"GET\",\"/courses-students\")\nt(\"GET\",\"/courses-students/filter\")\nt(\"GET\",\"/courses-students/labels\")\n\n# ── EDUCATION ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────\nprint(\"🎓 EDUCATION / LESSONS\")\nt(\"GET\",\"/lessons\")\nt(\"GET\",\"/lessons/detail-by-date\")\nt(\"GET\",\"/lesson-types\")\nt(\"GET\",\"/lesson-types/filter\")\nif ltid: t(\"GET\",f\"/lesson-types/{ltid}\")\n\nprint(\"👨‍🏫 TEACHER INFOS\")\nt(\"GET\",\"/teacher-infos\")\nt(\"GET\",\"/teacher-infos/ranking\")\n\nprint(\"📝 EXAMS\")\nt(\"GET\",\"/exams\")\nt(\"GET\",\"/exams/detail\")\nt(\"GET\",\"/exams/check-status-graduate\")\nt(\"GET\",\"/exam-results\")\nt(\"GET\",\"/exam-results/me\")\nt(\"GET\",\"/exam-schedules\")\nt(\"GET\",\"/exam-registrations\")\nt(\"GET\",\"/exam-registrations/me\")\n\nprint(\"📅 WORK CALENDARS\")\nt(\"GET\",\"/work-calendars\")\nif uid: t(\"GET\",f\"/work-calendars/users/{uid}\")\n\n# ── OPERATIONS ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────\nprint(\"🚗 VEHICLES\")\nt(\"GET\",\"/vehicles\")\nif cid: t(\"GET\",f\"/vehicles/{cid}/total-time\")\n\nprint(\"🏟️ STADIUMS\")\nt(\"GET\",\"/stadiums\")\nif sid: t(\"GET\",f\"/stadiums/{sid}\")\n\nprint(\"💰 PAYMENTS\")\nt(\"GET\",\"/payments\")\nt(\"GET\",\"/payments/total\")\n\nprint(\"🔖 LEAD SOURCES / INFOS\")\nt(\"GET\",\"/lead-sources\")\nt(\"GET\",\"/lead-infos\")\n\nprint(\"📊 INTERNAL COSTS\")\nt(\"GET\",\"/internal-cost-types\")\nt(\"GET\",\"/internal-costs/vehicle\")\nt(\"GET\",\"/internal-costs/office\")\nt(\"GET\",\"/internal-costs/vehicle/total\")\nt(\"GET\",\"/internal-costs/office/total\")\n\n# ── DASHBOARD ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────\nprint(\"📈 DASHBOARD\")\nt(\"GET\",\"/dashboards/reports/expenses\")\nt(\"GET\",\"/dashboards/reports/revenues\")\nt(\"GET\",\"/dashboards/reports/profits\")\n\n# ── NOTIFICATIONS ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────\nprint(\"🔔 NOTIFICATIONS\")\nt(\"GET\",\"/notify-configs\")\nt(\"GET\",\"/notify-contents\")\nt(\"GET\",\"/notify-users/unread/count\")\nt(\"GET\",\"/notifies\")\nt(\"GET\",\"/notifies/schedules\")\nt(\"GET\",\"/notifies/mobile\")\n\n# ── COMMENTS ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────\nprint(\"💬 COMMENTS\")\nt(\"GET\",\"/student-comments\")\nt(\"GET\",\"/teacher-comments\")\n\n# ── USERS SUB-ROUTES ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────\nprint(\"👨‍🎓 USERS / TEACHERS\")\nt(\"GET\",\"/users/teachers\")\nt(\"GET\",\"/users/students\")\nt(\"GET\",\"/users/sales\")\nt(\"GET\",\"/users/sales/counter\")\n\nif uid:\n    print(\"👨‍🎓 STUDENT routes (using uid)\")\n    t(\"GET\",f\"/users/students/{uid}\")\n    t(\"GET\",f\"/users/students/{uid}/lessons\")\n    t(\"GET\",f\"/users/students/{uid}/lessons/detail\")\n    t(\"GET\",f\"/users/students/{uid}/exams\")\n    t(\"GET\",f\"/users/students/{uid}/exams/detail\")\n    t(\"GET\",f\"/users/students/{uid}/payments\")\n    t(\"GET\",f\"/users/students/{uid}/payments/total\")\n\nif said:\n    print(\"💼 SALES routes (using said)\")\n    t(\"GET\",f\"/users/sales/{said}/info\")\n    t(\"GET\",f\"/users/sales/{said}/students\")\n    t(\"GET\",f\"/users/sales/{said}/payments\")\n\n# ── CONVENTIONS / IMPORTS ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────\nprint(\"📄 OTHER\")\nt(\"GET\",\"/conventions\")\nt(\"GET\",\"/imports\")\n\n# ── POST CREATE ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────\nprint(\"➕ CREATE (POST)\")\nt(\"POST\",\"/courses\",{\"code\":\"B2-2026-NEW\",\"course_fee\":15000000,\"status\":\"active\"})\nt(\"POST\",\"/stadiums\",{\"name\":\"Sân test 88\",\"locate\":\"https://maps.google.com/?q=11,107\"})\nt(\"POST\",\"/lesson-types\",{\"name\":\"Lý thuyết mới\",\"vehicle_apply\":\"car\",\"status\":\"active\",\"is_practice\":False})\nt(\"POST\",\"/internal-cost-types\",{\"name\":\"Chi phí test mới\"})\nt(\"POST\",\"/student-comments\",{\"comment\":\"Học sinh tốt\",\"rating\":5})\nt(\"POST\",\"/teacher-comments\",{\"comment\":\"Thầy giỏi\",\"rating\":5})\n\n# ── PATCH UPDATE ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────\nprint(\"✏️ UPDATE (PATCH)\")\nif cid: t(\"PATCH\",f\"/courses/{cid}\",{\"description\":\"Mô tả đã update\"})\nif sid: t(\"PATCH\",f\"/stadiums/{sid}\",{\"name\":\"Sân đổi tên thành công\"})\n\nprint(\"=\"*80)\nprint(f\"✅ OK: {OK}  ⚠️ WARN: {WARN}  ❌ ERR: {ERR}  | Total tested\")\nprint(\"=\"*80)\n"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":267,"output":2679,"cacheRead":42155,"cacheWrite":1786,"totalTokens":46887,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0