{"type":"message","id":"24183690","parentId":"604809e6","timestamp":"2026-04-14T07:42:19.544Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"No git in the DTLX BE workspace. So I can't commit. Let me just save the test results and report to the Lead.\n\nLet me now update MEMORY.md with the latest findings and save the comprehensive test results.","thinkingSignature":"12f4eab89d3ea51aa14f55b37ab447170779548106973039b5275b9ae6bc36f0"},{"type":"text","text":"Không có git trong workspace — save kết quả test:\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_7cb1sy9bbkko_1","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/master-orchestrator/memory/2026-04-14-dtlx-api-test.md","content":"# DTLX BE — Full API Test Report 2026-04-14\n\n## Kết quả tổng quan\n- **Tested:** 79 endpoints\n- **✅ OK:** 67\n- **⚠️ WARN:** 11 (validation/expected 404)\n- **❌ ERR:** 1 (sales/counter — ĐÃ FIX)\n\n## Bugs ĐÃ Fix\n\n### 1. `/reports/profits` → 500 ❌ → ✅\n- **File:** `ahv-dtlx-backend/src/modules/coursesStudents/coursesStudents.service.ts` (line ~774)\n- **Bug:** `docTotalFee[0].total_received_fee` crash khi aggregate trả về array rỗng\n- **Fix:** Thêm `?? 0` guard\n\n### 2. `/notify-users/unread/count` → 500 ❌ → ✅\n- **File:** `ahv-dtlx-backend/src/modules/notifyUsers/notifyUsers.controller.ts`\n- **Bug:** `String(req.query.user_id)` = undefined → `ObjectId(\"undefined\")` crash\n- **Fix:** Fallback về `req.user.id` từ JWT\n\n### 3. `/users/sales/counter` → 500 ❌ → ✅\n- **File:** `ahv-dtlx-backend/src/modules/users/users.service.ts` (lines 882, 1040)\n- **Bug:** `docCounter[0].totalLead` crash khi aggregate trả về `[]`\n- **Fix:** `docCounter[0] || { totalLead: 0, totalContract: 0 }`\n\n### 4. `/lessons/detail-by-date` route crash → ✅ FIXED\n- **File:** `ahv-dtlx-backend/src/modules/lessons/lessons.route.ts`\n- **Bug:** Route `/:id` catch-all được mount TRƯỚC `/detail-by-date` → `GET /lessons/detail` bị route `/:id` bắt, cast \"detail\" → ObjectId → crash → server die\n- **Fix:** Reorder routes — move `GET /` lên trước `GET /:id`\n\n### 5. `/teacher-infos` → 404 → ✅\n- **File:** `ahv-dtlx-backend/src/modules/teacherInfos/teacherInfos.route.ts`\n- **Bug:** Không có `router.get('/')` — chỉ có `/ranking`, `/:id`, `/user/:userId`\n- **Fix:** Thêm `router.get('/', teacherInfosController.getTeacherRanking)`\n\n## ⚠️ WARN — Expected Behavior (không phải bug)\n| Endpoint | Status | Nguyên nhân |\n|---|---|---|\n| `PATCH /auth/change-password` | 400 | Thiếu required fields (oldPassword/newPassword format) |\n| `POST /auth/refetch-token` | 403 | Refresh token expired — đúng behavior |\n| `GET /exam-results/me` | 404 | Không có exam_result cho user hiện tại |\n| `GET /users/teachers` | 404 | Không có role \"teacher\" trong DB |\n| `GET /users/students` | 404 | Không có role \"student\" trong DB |\n| `GET /conventions` | 404 | Convention module chỉ có POST, không có GET |\n| `GET /imports` | 404 | Imports module chỉ có POST (upload file), không có GET |\n| `POST /student-comments` | 400 | Thiếu required fields (student_id, rating) |\n| `POST /teacher-comments` | 400 | Thiếu required fields (teacher_id, rating) |\n| `POST /courses` (lần 2) | 400 | Mã khóa học đã tồn tại |\n\n## Data hiện có trong DB\n| Collection | Số docs | Fields trả về |\n|---|---|---|\n| courses | 4 | id, code, course_fee, status, license_category_id, description |\n| stadiums | 2 | id, name, locate (URL), note, status |\n| lesson-types | 3 | id, name, status, is_practice, is_exam, vehicle_apply, price |\n| roles | 2 | role_name |\n| agents | 1 | id, name, description |\n| lead-sources | 2 | id, name, description |\n| internal-cost-types | 4 | id, name, description, is_vehicle |\n| users | 1 | _id, username, email, full_name, phone, gender, status, role_names |\n\n## Response Structure Patterns\n| Pattern | Modules |\n|---|---|\n| `{ docs: [], meta: {...} }` | courses, stadiums, vehicles, payments, lessons, exams, comments |\n| `{ data: [], meta: {...} }` | license-categories, lesson-types, log-tasks |\n| `{ result: [], meta: {...} }` | lead-sources, lead-infos, notifies |\n| `{ doc: {...} }` | Course/Stadium/LessonType detail, auth signin |\n| `{ revenue/expense/profits/arData, meta }` | Dashboard profits |\n| `{ statistics: {...}, data, meta }` | Exam-registrations |\n\n## Backend Status\n- **Port:** 3001\n- **Build:** ✅ Passing (yarn build — 31s)\n- **Running:** ✅ PID 124614 (restarted with fixes)\n- **Database:** MongoDB `dtlx` on port 27017\n"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":115,"output":1327,"cacheRead":79777,"cacheWrite":403,"totalTokens":81622,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776152511694,"responseId":"062d22c147f4a033c94c4723f6d565f6"}}
