{"type":"message","id":"76c4afe7","parentId":"eb58cd29","timestamp":"2026-04-14T07:42:32.939Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now let me give the Lead a clear summary of the findings.","thinkingSignature":"269769f8b62f3dddabcded74b3b6aae5f087f7c518d008cd3b108e25410c8908"},{"type":"text","text":"---\n\n## 🌐 Orbis — DTLX BE Full API Test Report\n\n**Tested: 79 endpoints | ✅ 67 OK | ⚠️ 11 WARN | ❌ 0 ERR**\n\n### Bugs ĐÃ FIX (4 bugs)\n\n| # | Endpoint | Before | After | Fix |\n|---|---|---|---|---|\n| 1 | `/reports/profits` | 500 | ✅ | `?? 0` guard — aggregate empty array |\n| 2 | `/notify-users/unread/count` | 500 | ✅ | Fallback `req.user.id` — query undefined |\n| 3 | `/users/sales/counter` | 500 | ✅ | `docCounter[0] || {}` — empty result |\n| 4 | `/lessons/detail-by-date` | **Server crash** | ✅ | Route reorder — `/:id` catchall moved after specific routes |\n\n### ⚠️ WARN (11 endpoints — expected behavior, not bugs)\n\n- `PATCH /auth/change-password` → 400: thiếu required fields\n- `POST /auth/refetch-token` → 403: token expired (đúng spec)\n- `GET /users/students`, `/users/teachers` → 404: chưa có role student/teacher trong DB\n- `GET /exam-results/me` → 404: user chưa có exam result\n- `GET /conventions`, `/imports` → 404: module chỉ có POST (gửi notification / import file)\n- `POST /student-comments`, `POST /teacher-comments` → 400: thiếu required fields\n\n### Response Structure Patterns\n- **Phổ biến nhất:** `{ docs: [], meta: { totalItems, itemCount, itemsPerPage, currentPage, totalPages } }`\n- **Dashboard:** `{ revenue/expense/profits/arData: [], meta: { totalRevenue, totalExpense, totalProfits } }`\n- **Auth signin:** `{ doc: {...user}, permissions: [], accessToken, refreshToken }`\n\n**Backend đang chạy port 3001 ✅**"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":153,"output":465,"cacheRead":79916,"cacheWrite":1609,"totalTokens":82143,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cac