ehind 11 commits, FE synced\\n- Today (2026-04-13): Fix AHV Works P0 issues (13 items), Stitch MCP wrapper test, stitch-connect skill update, BE merge decision pending\\n- Blockers: BE is 11 commits behind remote on notification system, Lead decision needed for merge\\n\\nCurrent time is 10:00 PM UTC (10:00 PM Monday April 13), so this briefing covers the day and sets up for Tuesday.\\n\\n\\nNow I'll format this as a status report.\"\n            },\n            {\n              \"type\": \"text\",\n              \"text\": \"🌅 **ORBIS MORNING BRIEFING**\\n📅 Monday, April 13, 2026\\n⏰ 10:00 PM UTC | 5:00 AM UTC+7\\n\\n━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━\\n\\n**1️⃣ YESTERDAY'S COMPLETED TASKS**\\n\\n✅ **AHV Works Review** — FULL REVIEW COMPLETE (commit 84cdb2d)\\n✅ **Session Recovery** — Crash at 00:34 UTC (HTTP 500 / context overflow), fully recovered on model `AHV-Holding-DEV`\\n✅ **FE Sync** — Frontend fully synchronized with remote develop ✅\\n✅ **DTLX/QLHV Systems** — Stable, shared DB architecture operational\\n✅ **34-Agent Ecosystem** — SKILL_GATES, HANDOVER/FEEDBACK, OPENSPEC all verified ✅\\n\\n━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━\\n\\n**2️⃣ TODAY'S PRIORITIES**\\n\\n🔴 **P0 — AHV Works Fixes** — 13 unresolved P0 issues queued for resolution\\n🟡 **Stitch MCP Wrapper** — Complete integration testing post-gateway restart\\n🟡 **stitch-connect Skill** — Update to use MCP wrapper (replacing OAuth flow)\\n🔵 **BE Notification System** — Local behind remote by 11 commits; notification system feature pending merge\\n\\n━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━\\n\\n**3️⃣ BLOCKERS & RISKS**\\n\\n⚠️ **BE Merge Conflict** — Backend is 11 commits behind remote on `notification-system`; remote is 2 commits ahead on `data-isolation`. **Lead decision required** before merge can proceed.\\n\\n⚠️ **Context Overflow Risk** — Session crash root cause identified (200k+ tokens / model instability). Monitor session health closely.\\n\\n━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━\\n\\n**Pipeline Status:** 🟢 HEALTHY\\n**Active Agents:** 34 (v4 ecosystem)