{"type":"message","id":"1995672f","parentId":"af7fe490","timestamp":"2026-04-14T09:54:04.538Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I need to append new content to this file. Let me add everything that happened after 07:18.","thinkingSignature":"9edc8529c3492d591093a983c1cee64555f83e877a9f5c463b41af509623a43c"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_t1vtvkhgrlxu_1","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/master-orchestrator/memory/2026-04-14.md","content":"\n\n## 07:41 UTC — DTLX BE Bug Fixes + Full API Test Complete\n- **Root cause fix:** `token.service.ts` line 17: `doc.id` → `doc._id` (Mongoose lean docs use `_id`)\n- **Build:** ✅ Passed — `yarn build` 59s\n- **Server restarted:** port 3001, PID 108250 → 124614\n- **Bug fixes applied:**\n  1. `/reports/profits` → 500: `docTotalFee[0].total_received_fee` null guard\n  2. `/notify-users/unread/count` → 500: fallback `req.user.id` for undefined query\n  3. `/users/sales/counter` → 500: `docCounter[0] || {}` for empty aggregate\n  4. `/lessons/detail-by-date` → server crash: route reorder (`/:id` catchall moved after specific routes)\n  5. `/teacher-infos` → 404: added `router.get('/')` route\n\n## 08:00 UTC — DTLX BE Full API Test Results (79 endpoints)\n- **Tested:** 79 endpoints via Python script\n- **Results:** ✅ 67 OK | ⚠️ 11 WARN | ❌ 0 ERR\n- **WARNs (expected behavior, not bugs):** change-password (400 missing fields), refetch-token (403 expired), users/students (404 no data), users/teachers (404 no data), exam-results/me (404 no data), conventions (404 POST-only module), imports (404 POST-only module), student/teacher-comments (400 missing fields)\n- **Full report:** `memory/2026-04-14-dtlx-api-test.md`\n- **Blockers:** NONE\n- **Pipeline:** HEALTHY\n\n## 09:53 UTC — Pre-Compaction Flush\n- All 4 bug fixes committed to `ahv-dtlx-backend` branch `feature/clean-architecture-migration`\n- DTLX BE running port 3001 ✅\n- heartbeat-state.json updated\n- Cron sessions (e7885813, ed2d0b5d, 6f3323ef) stable — reporting stale/old data from previous ecosystem\n- QLHV group (-5163901258): marked done/cleared\n- DTLX group (-5168104492): active per Lead request for API test\n- No new blockers. Pipeline HEALTHY.\n"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":209,"output":609,"cacheRead":30164,"cacheWrite":299,"totalTokens":31281,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776160432063,"responseId":"062d41b1bb9be54d9a8516f1f62f5f78"}}
