{"type":"message","id":"96552374","parentId":"77d93834","timestamp":"2026-04-14T10:07:41.948Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"OK, I can see the full picture now. The issue is clear:\n\n1. All data was wiped when MongoDB was reset (database is now empty - no courses, no stadiums, etc.)\n2. POST works - we can create new data (courses, stadiums, lesson-types, internal-cost-types all created)\n3. But the data from the previous session was lost (DB reset likely happened when Docker container restarted or something)\n\nNow I need to seed data so the GET endpoints return actual data. The Lead specifically wants to see data returned. Let me:\n\n1. First, seed a comprehensive set of data\n2. Then run the full test again to show actual data\n\n\n3. Create realistic seed data for all major entities\n\nI should build a comprehensive seed script that populates courses, stadiums, lesson types, internal cost types, lead sources, and users with the necessary roles and permissions.","thinkingSignature":"13f580f95c493ecf7d92390c88109d11aaa5d51c880a10e87304c6ff4933547c"},{"type":"text","text":"Vấn đề rõ ràng rồi — **database bị reset**, toàn bộ data lost. Cần seed lại để GET trả về data thực:\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_0if2j1aau662_1","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"/tmp/dtlx-seed-realistic.py","content":"#!/usr/bin/env python3\n\"\"\"Seed realistic data for DTLX BE testing\"\"\"\nimport json, urllib.request, urllib.error\n\nBASE = \"http://localhost:3001/api/v1\"\n\ndef api(m, p, t=None, b=None):\n    url = BASE+p; h={\"Content-Type\":\"application/json\"}\n    if t: h[\"Authorization\"]=f\"Bearer {t}\"\n    req = urllib.request.Request(url, data=json.dumps(b).encode() if b else None, headers=h, method=m)\n    try:\n        r=urllib.request.urlopen(req,timeout=20)\n        return r.status, json.loads(r.read())\n    except urllib.error.HTTPError as e:\n        return e.code, e.read()[:500].decode(\"utf-8\",\"replace\")\n    except Exception as e:\n        return 0, str(e)[:80]\n\n_, r = api(\"POST\",\"/auth/signin\",None,{\"username\":\"admin2\",\"password\":\"Password123@\"})\ntoken = r[\"data\"][\"accessToken\"]\n\ndef post(path, body, desc):\n    s, r = api(\"POST\", path, token, body)\n    if s in (200,201):\n        doc = r.get(\"data\",{}).get(\"doc\",{})\n        new_id = doc.get(\"id\") or doc.get(\"_id\",\"?\")\n        print(f\"  ✅ Created {desc}: id={new_id}\")\n        return new_id\n    else:\n        msg = r.get(\"message\",\"\") if isinstance(r,dict) else str(r)[:60]\n        print(f\"  ❌ FAIL {desc}: [{s}] {msg[:80]}\")\n        return None\n\ndef get_id(path):\n    s, r = api(\"GET\", path, token)\n    if s == 200:\n        d = r.get(\"data\",{})\n        docs = d.get(\"docs\",d.get(\"data\",d.get(\"result\",[])))\n        if docs and len(docs) > 0:\n            return docs[0].get(\"id\") or docs[0].get(\"_id\")\n    return None\n\nprint(\"=== SEEDING DTLX DATA ===\\n\")\n\n# 1. License Categories\nprint(\"1️⃣ License Categories\")\nlc_b2 = post(\"/license-categories\", {\"name\":\"Bằng B2\",\"code\":\"B2\",\"fee\":15000000,\"vehicle_type\":\"car\",\"lessons\":[]},\"LicenseCat B2\")\nlc_a1 = post(\"/license-categories\", {\"name\":\"Bằng A1\",\"code\":\"A1\",\"fee\":8000000,\"vehicle_type\":\"motorcycle\",\"lessons\":[]},\"LicenseCat A1\")\nlc_c    = post(\"/license-categories\", {\"name\":\"Bằng C\",\"code\":\"C\",\"fee\":25000000,\"vehicle_type\":\"truck\",\"lessons\":[]},\"LicenseCat C\")\n\n# 2. Lesson Types\nprint(\"\\n2️⃣ Lesson Types\")\nlt1 = post(\"/lesson-types\",{\"name\":\"Lý thuyết\",\"vehicle_apply\":\"car\",\"status\":\"active\",\"is_practice\":False,\"is_exam\":False,\"price\":500000},\"LessonType Lý thuyết\")\nlt2 = post(\"/lesson-types\",{\"name\":\"Thực hành\",\"vehicle_apply\":\"car\",\"status\":\"active\",\"is_practice\":True,\"is_exam\":False,\"price\":2000000},\"LessonType Thực hành\")\nlt3 = post(\"/lesson-types\",{\"name\":\"Thi sát hạch\",\"vehicle_apply\":\"car\",\"status\":\"active\",\"is_practice\":False,\"is_exam\":True,\"price\":0},\"LessonType Thi\")\n\n# 3. Stadiums\nprint(\"\\n3️⃣ Stadiums\")\ns1 = post(\"/stadiums\",{\"name\":\"Sân tập lái xe Quận 1\",\"locate\":\"https://maps.google.com/?q=10.775,106.700\",\"note\":\"Sân rộng 2000m2\",\"status\":\"active\"})\ns2 = post(\"/stadiums\",{\"name\":\"Sân tập lái xe Quận 7\",\"locate\":\"https://maps.google.com/?q=10.738,106.730\",\"note\":\"Sân có mái che\",\"status\":\"active\"})\n\n# 4. Courses\nprint(\"\\n4️⃣ Courses\")\nc1 = post(\"/courses\",{\"code\":\"B2-2026-Q1\",\"course_fee\":15000000,\"status\":\"active\",\"description\":\"Khóa học B2 Quý 1/2026\",\"license_category_id\":lc_b2})\nc2 = post(\"/courses\",{\"code\":\"A1-2026-Q1\",\"course_fee\":8000000,\"status\":\"active\",\"description\":\"Khóa học A1 Quý 1/2026\",\"license_category_id\":lc_a1})\nc3 = post(\"/courses\",{\"code\":\"C-2026-Q1\",\"course_fee\":25000000,\"status\":\"active\",\"description\":\"Khóa học C Quý 1/2026\",\"license_category_id\":lc_c})\n\n# 5. Internal Cost Types\nprint(\"\\n5️⃣ Internal Cost Types\")\nict1 = post(\"/internal-cost-types\",{\"name\":\"Chi phí xăng xe\",\"description\":\"Chi phí nhiên liệu cho xe tập\",\"is_vehicle\":True})\nict2 = post(\"/internal-cost-types\",{\"name\":\"Chi phí điện nước\",\"description\":\"Chi phí điện nước văn phòng\",\"is_vehicle\":False})\nict3 = post(\"/internal-cost-types\",{\"name\":\"Lương giáo viên\",\"description\":\"Lương giáo viên dạy lái\",\"is_vehicle\":False})\n\n# 6. Lead Sources\nprint(\"\\n6️⃣ Lead Sources\")\nls1 = post(\"/lead-sources\",{\"name\":\"Google Ads\",\"description\":\"Từ quảng cáo Google\"},\"LeadSource Google\")\nls2 = post(\"/lead-sources\",{\"name\":\"Facebook\",\"description\":\"Từ fanpage Facebook\"},\"LeadSource Facebook\")\nls3 = post(\"/lead-sources\",{\"name\":\"Giới thiệu\",\"description\":\"Học viên giới thiệu\"},\"LeadSource Referral\")\n\n# 7. Internal Costs (Vehicle)\nprint(\"\\n7️⃣ Internal Costs (Vehicle)\")\n# Need valid ObjectIds for vehicle costs\n# We'll just note that vehicle costs need vehicle_id which requires vehicle seeding\n# For now, just create office costs\nfor i,amount,name in [\n    (\"Chi phí xăng tháng 1/2026\", 5000000),\n    (\"Chi phí xăng tháng 2/2026\", 4500000),\n    (\"Chi phí sửa chữa xe\", 2000000),\n]:\n    s, r = api(\"POST\",\"/internal-costs/vehicle\",token,{\n        \"internal_cost_type_id\": ict1,\n        \"amount\": amount,\n        \"description\": i,\n        \"date\": \"2026-01-15\"\n    })\n    if s in (200,201): print(f\"  ✅ Vehicle cost: {i}\")\n    else: print(f\"  ❌ [{s}] Vehicle cost: {r.get('message','')[:50]}\")\n\n# 8. Internal Costs (Office)\nfor i,amount in [\n    (\"Tiền điện tháng 1/2026\", 3000000),\n    (\"Tiền nước tháng 1/2026\", 1000000),\n    (\"Lương giáo viên tháng 1/2026\", 50000000),\n]:\n    s, r = api(\"POST\",\"/internal-costs/office\",token,{\n        \"internal_cost_type_id\": ict2 if \"điện\" in i or \"nước\" in i else ict3,\n        \"amount\": amount,\n        \"description\": i,\n        \"date\": \"2026-01-31\"\n    })\n    if s in (200,201): print(f\"  ✅ Office cost: {i}\")\n    else: print(f\"  ❌ [{s}] Office cost: {r.get('message','')[:50]}\")\n\n# 9. Payments (need course_student_id — we'll create courses-students first)\nprint(\"\\n8️⃣ Course Students + Payments\")\n# Create course-student records\nfor i in range(3):\n    s, r = api(\"POST\",\"/courses-students\",token,{\n        \"course_id\": c1,\n        \"student_id\": \"69de0f47cd1429323e44ba89\",  # admin user\n        \"received_fee\": 15000000,\n        \"paid_fee\": 10000000 if i < 2 else 15000000,\n        \"status\": \"studying\" if i < 2 else \"completed\"\n    })\n    if s in (200,201):\n        cs_id = r.get(\"data\",{}).get(\"doc\",{}).get(\"id\") or r.get(\"data\",{}).get(\"ids\",[][0] if r.get(\"data\",{}).get(\"ids\") else None)\n        print(f\"  ✅ CourseStudent: {cs_id}\")\n        # Create payment\n        s2, r2 = api(\"POST\",\"/payments\",token,{\n            \"course_student_id\": cs_id,\n            \"amount\": 5000000,\n            \"payment_method\": \"cash\",\n            \"note\": f\"Thanh toán đợt {i+1}\"\n        })\n        if s2 in (200,201): print(f\"    ✅ Payment: {r2.get('data',{}).get('doc',{}).get('id','?')}\")\n        else: print(f\"    ❌ Payment: [{s2}] {r2.get('message','')[:40]}\")\n    else:\n        print(f\"  ❌ [{s}] CourseStudent: {r.get('message','')[:50]}\")\n\n# 10. Work Calendars\nprint(\"\\n9️⃣ Work Calendars\")\nfor day, status, note in [\n    (\"2026-01-06\",\"working\",\"Ca sáng 8h-12h\"),\n    (\"2026-01-07\",\"working\",\"Ca chiều 13h-17h\"),\n    (\"2026-01-08\",\"working\",\"Ca tối 18h-21h\"),\n]:\n    s, r = api(\"POST\",\"/work-calendars\",token,{\n        \"user_id\": \"69de0f47cd1429323e44ba89\",\n        \"day\": day,\n        \"status\": status,\n        \"note\": note\n    })\n    if s in (200,201): print(f\"  ✅ WorkCalendar: {day}\")\n    else: print(f\"  ❌ [{s}] WorkCalendar: {r.get('message','')[:50]}\")\n\n# 11. Exams\nprint(\"\\n🔟 Exams\")\nex1 = post(\"/exams\",{\"course_id\":c1,\"exam_date\":\"2026-03-15\",\"location\":\"Trường ĐH GTVT\",\"status\":\"scheduled\",\"total_slot\":50},\"Exam B2 Q1\")\nex2 = post(\"/exams\",{\"course_id\":c2,\"exam_date\":\"2026-03-16\",\"location\":\"Sở GTVT\",\"status\":\"scheduled\",\"total_slot\":30},\"Exam A1 Q1\")\n\n# 12. Exam Schedules\nprint(\"\\n1️⃣1️⃣ Exam Schedules\")\nes1 = post(\"/exam-schedules\",{\"course_id\":c1,\"exam_date\":\"2026-03-15\",\"start_time\":\"08:00\",\"end_time\":\"10:00\",\"location\":\"Phòng thi 101\"},\"ExamSchedule B2\")\nes2 = post(\"/exam-schedules\",{\"course_id\":c2,\"exam_date\":\"2026-03-16\",\"start_time\":\"14:00\",\"end_time\":\"16:00\",\"location\":\"Phòng thi 102\"},\"ExamSchedule A1\")\n\n# 13. Lessons\nprint(\"\\n1️⃣2️⃣ Lessons\")\nfor i,date,slot in [(\"2026-02-01\",\"Ca 1: 8h-10h\"),(\"2026-02-03\",\"Ca 2: 14h-16h\"),(\"2026-02-05\",\"Ca 1: 8h-10h\")]:\n    s, r = api(\"POST\",\"/lessons\",token,{\n        \"course_student_id\": None,  # would need valid cs id\n        \"lesson_type_id\": lt2,\n        \"stadium_id\": s1,\n        \"teacher_id\": \"69de0f47cd1429323e44ba89\",\n        \"day\": date,\n        \"time_slot\": slot,\n        \"status\": \"scheduled\",\n        \"is_practice\": True\n    })\n    if s in (200,201): print(f\"  ✅ Lesson: {date}\")\n    else: print(f\"  ❌ [{s}] Lesson: {r.get('message','')[:60]}\")\n\n# 14. Student Comments\nprint(\"\\n1️⃣3️⃣ Student Comments\")\ns, r = api(\"POST\",\"/student-comments\",token,{\n    \"student_id\": \"69de0f47cd1429323e44ba89\",\n    \"comment\": \"Khóa học rất bổ ích, giáo viên nhiệt tình\",\n    \"rating\": 5\n})\nif s in (200,201): print(f\"  ✅ StudentComment created\")\nelse: print(f\"  ❌ [{s}] StudentComment: {r.get('message','')[:60]}\")\n\n# 15. Teacher Comments\ns, r = api(\"POST\",\"/teacher-comments\",token,{\n    \"teacher_id\": \"69de0f47cd1429323e44ba89\",\n    \"comment\": \"Học viên tiến bộ rất nhanh\",\n    \"rating\": 5\n})\nif s in (200,201): print(f\"  ✅ TeacherComment created\")\nelse: print(f\"  ❌ [{s}] TeacherComment: {r.get('message','')[:60]}\")\n\nprint(\"\\n=== SEEDING COMPLETE ===\")\nprint(\"\\nNow re-running full API test with data...\")\n"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":2483,"output":3364,"cacheRead":101351,"cacheWrite":7387,"totalTokens":114585,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776161200392,"responseId":"062d44b233cf0aecffafd6034ae3d082"}}
