{"type":"message","id":"d04fc9ea","parentId":"df589dce","timestamp":"2026-04-14T10:07:48.963Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_q2tln1bn8imw_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"=== SEEDING DTLX DATA ===\n\n1️⃣ License Categories\n  ❌ FAIL LicenseCat B2: [400] {\"status\":\"error\",\"message\":\"Validation Failed\",\"err\":{\"name\n  ❌ FAIL LicenseCat A1: [400] {\"status\":\"error\",\"message\":\"Validation Failed\",\"err\":{\"name\n  ❌ FAIL LicenseCat C: [400] {\"status\":\"error\",\"message\":\"Validation Failed\",\"err\":{\"name\n\n2️⃣ Lesson Types\n  ✅ Created LessonType Lý thuyết: id=69de11f4dc29eb09e5c4f041\n  ✅ Created LessonType Thực hành: id=69de11f4dc29eb09e5c4f048\n  ✅ Created LessonType Thi: id=69de11f4dc29eb09e5c4f04f\n\n3️⃣ Stadiums\n\n(Command exited with code 1)"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":1,"durationMs":1047,"aggregated":"=== SEEDING DTLX DATA ===\n\n1️⃣ License Categories\n  ❌ FAIL LicenseCat B2: [400] {\"status\":\"error\",\"message\":\"Validation Failed\",\"err\":{\"name\n  ❌ FAIL LicenseCat A1: [400] {\"status\":\"error\",\"message\":\"Validation Failed\",\"err\":{\"name\n  ❌ FAIL LicenseCat C: [400] {\"status\":\"error\",\"message\":\"Validation Failed\",\"err\":{\"name\n\n2️⃣ Lesson Types\n  ✅ Created LessonType Lý thuyết: id=69de11f4dc29eb09e5c4f041\n  ✅ Created LessonType Thực hành: id=69de11f4dc29eb09e5c4f048\n  ✅ Created LessonType Thi: id=69de11f4dc29eb09e5c4f04f\n\n3️⃣ Stadiums\n\n(Command exited with code 1)","cwd":"/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/master-orchestrator"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1776161268783}}
{"type":"message","id":"9febad5e","parentId":"d04fc9ea","timestamp":"2026-04-14T10:08:00.854Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Many things are failing. The issues are:\n\n1. License Categories validation: needs `fee, vehicle_type, lessons` — not `name, code`\n2. Stadiums validation: `locate` needs to be a valid URL format\n3. Courses validation: need specific fields\n4. Internal Costs: need `internal_cost_type_id` as ObjectId — but we're passing the string we got from POST\n\nLet me check the exact validation requirements for each endpoint and seed correctly.","thinkingSignature":"690e180259f912d319812559320a131b5df246350b936f45c1bda51fcf088980"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_26xyo9vfrmkp_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"python3 << 'PYEOF'\nimport json, urllib.request, urllib.error\n\nBASE = \"http://localhost:3001/api/v1\"\ndef api(m, p, t=None, b=None):\n    url = BASE+p; h={\"Content-Type\":\"application/json\"}\n    if t: h[\"Authorization\"]=f\"Bearer {t}\"\n    req = urllib.request.Request(url, data=json.dumps(b).encode() if b else None, headers=h, method=m)\n    try:\n        r=urllib.request.urlopen(req,timeout=20)\n        return r.status, json.loads(r.read())\n    except urllib.error.HTTPError as e:\n        body = e.read()[:500].decode(\"utf-8\",\"replace\")\n        return e.code, body\n    except Exception as e:\n        return 0, str(e)\n\n_, r = api(\"POST\",\"/auth/signin\",None,{\"username\":\"admin2\",\"password\":\"Password123@\"})\ntoken = r[\"data\"][\"accessToken\"]\n\n# Check validation errors for each failing endpoint\nfor path,body,desc in [\n    (\"/license-categories\",{\"name\":\"B2\",\"code\":\"B2\",\"fee\":15000000},\"LicenseCat\"),\n    (\"/stadiums\",{\"name\":\"Sân 1\",\"locate\":\"https://maps.google.com/?q=10,106\"},\"Stadium\"),\n    (\"/courses\",{\"code\":\"B2-2026-01\",\"course_fee\":15000000,\"status\":\"active\"},\"Course\"),\n]:\n    s,r2 = api(\"POST\",path,token,body)\n    if s not in (200,201):\n        try:\n            rj = json.loads(r2)\n            err = rj.get(\"err\",{})\n            details = err.get(\"details\",[])\n            if isinstance(details,list):\n                for d in details[:3]:\n                    print(f\"FAIL {desc}: [{d.get('path','')}] {d.get('message','')}\")\n            else:\n                print(f\"FAIL {desc}: {err}\")\n        except:\n            print(f\"FAIL {desc}: {r2[:200]}\")\nPYEOF","timeout":20}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":308,"output":577,"cacheRead":111119,"cacheWrite":3479,"totalTokens":115483,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776161269020,"responseId":"062d44f615666f755ab7765feb921463"}}
