{"type":"message","id":"0fcbbeb7","parentId":"570ce17e","timestamp":"2026-04-14T10:21:13.702Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Looking at the pipelines, I can see:\n\n1. Most recent pipelines are from late March 2026 (dates are like `2026-03-30`, `2026-03-27`, `2026-03-26`) - these are from about 2 weeks ago.\n2. No running pipelines currently\n3. The latest pipelines are:\n   - Pipeline 2416857386 (MR !269) - success - 2026-03-30\n   - Pipeline 2416854588 (MR !166) - success - 2026-03-30\n   - Several failed pipelines from MR !166 around the same time\n\nThe timestamps are confusing - they show dates in March 2026, which is in the past. \n\nWait, I'm realizing these timestamps are actually from the future relative to today (2026-04-14), so they're likely just archived or old data. More importantly, I'm noticing the pipeline execution times are quite fast - around 2-3 minutes - which suggests the runner itself isn't slow. Let me dig into the MR !167 that's still open and see what's happening with the feature branch.","thinkingSignature":"cfa5ac7b797a6cb68da94cede50ff7b27bde52a825803e907ed0ad1ca1e6041b"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_gddqq2wrxpcs_1","name":"gitlab__gitlab_list_merge_requests","arguments":{"project_id":"77055841","state":"opened"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":3604,"output":279,"cacheRead":134234,"cacheWrite":151,"totalTokens":138268,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776162061838,"responseId":"062d480ff340050b165084b1d1517f4b"}}
