{"type":"message","id":"56198dd5","parentId":"9c80c8de","timestamp":"2026-04-14T11:38:46.794Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The QLHV group session is actually just echoing heartbeat responses — it's not doing real work. It's a stale session that was never properly stopped. It keeps responding \"HEARTBEAT_OK\". This is not real work.\n\nThe cron reports show \"Tuition work, 4 sub-agents\" but the actual session content shows only heartbeat echo. The 4 sub-agents listed are old stale sub-agents from the previous session.\n\nI should note this in the heartbeat state. But for now — HEARTBEAT_OK since it's just echoing heartbeats and not causing any harm. The pipeline is healthy.","thinkingSignature":"3a53ddf955b1cc4dd67c13cbccc26f56873dfb740a218c074c3522143f8e6eec"},{"type":"text","text":"HEARTBEAT_OK\n\n*QLHV group session (-5163901258) chỉ đang echo heartbeat, không có task thực. Pipeline healthy.*"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":826,"output":162,"cacheRead":143831,"cacheWrite":1121,"totalTokens":145940,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776166719638,"responseId":"062d5a4152722622bc8ee732381bbb32"}}
